As%20you%20can%20tell%20from%20our%20bold%20new%20logo%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22black%20Business%20Insider%20logo%20on%20white%20background%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6553662b385143459e8c6d42%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20you%20can%20see%2C%20I%20am%20fired%20up%20to%20be%20Business%20Insider%20again!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20while%20it%20was%20wonderful%20to%20be%20Insider%20%E2%80%94%20we%20introduced%20ourselves%20to%20new%20audiences%2C%20and%20we%20won%20a%20Pulitzer%20and%20two%20Emmys%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20now%20about%20recommitting%20to%20what%20we%20do%20best%3A%20our%20powerful%2C%20insightful%2C%20and%20unique%20coverage%20of%20business%2C%20tech%2C%20and%20innovation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20world%20where%20trust%20in%20the%20media%20is%20at%20an%20all-time%20low%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.yougov.com%2Fpolitics%2Farticles%2F45671-trust-in-media-2023-what-news-outlets-trust-poll%3Fredirect_from%3D%252Ftopics%252Fpolitics%252Farticles-reports%252F2023%252F05%252F08%252F2023-trust-in-media-what-news-outlets-trust-poll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3EBusiness%20Insider%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20publications%20trusted%20across%20party%20lines%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBusiness%20Insider%20is%20a%20widely%20recognized%20name%20that%20gets%20sources%20on%20the%20phone%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0helping%20us%20do%20better%20journalism%20for%20you.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20of%20all%2C%20I'm%20excited%20about%20the%20new%20name%20because%20it's%20a%20name%20that%20reminds%20us%20all%20that%20Business%20Insider%20isn't%20some%20generic%20news%20website%20built%20for%20everybody.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20built%20for%20people%20who%20read%20our%20journalism%20because%20it%20helps%20them%20grow%20professionally%C2%A0%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20personally.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20built%20for%20people%20who%20want%20society%20to%20advance%20and%20believe%20business%20and%20innovative%20thinking%20can%20drive%20positive%20change.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20built%20for%20people%20who%20want%20to%20win%2C%20but%20don't%20believe%20that%20means%20everyone%20else%20has%20to%20lose.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20built%20for%20people%20who%20are%20as%20ambitious%20for%20life%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0love%2C%20travel%2C%20food%2C%20and%20adventure!%20%E2%80%94%20as%20they%20are%20for%20work.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20built%20for%20you!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20what%20can%20you%20expect%20from%20us%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20Business%20Insider%2C%20we're%20dedicated%20to%20providing%20you%20with%20journalism%20that%20isn't%20just%20informative%20but%20transformative.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou're%20not%20just%20looking%20for%20news%3B%20you're%20seeking%20insights%20that%20give%20you%20an%20edge%20in%20a%20rapidly%20evolving%20world.%20You%20want%20in-depth%20coverage%20of%20business%2C%20technology%2C%20and%20innovation%20%E2%80%94%20the%20fields%20that%20shape%20our%20future.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20that's%20exactly%20what%20we'll%20deliver%3A%20stories%20that%20dig%20deeper%20into%20the%20trends%20and%20innovations%20driving%20global%20markets%20and%20the%20economy%2C%20with%20a%20sharp%20focus%20on%20sectors%20most%20transformed%20by%20technology.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20we%20know%20your%20interests%20don't%20end%20there.%20Your%20life%20outside%20work%20is%20just%20as%20dynamic%20and%20full%20of%20ambition.%20That's%20why%20our%20coverage%20extends%20to%20health%2C%20parenting%2C%20science%2C%20entertainment%2C%20food%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20lot%20of%20publications%20cover%20those%20topics%2C%20but%20we%20do%20it%20for%20people%20who%20want%20to%20squeeze%20the%20most%20out%20of%20life%20and%20who%20are%20forward-thinking%20optimists%2C%20hungry%20for%20change%20and%20innovation.%20Expect%20evidence-based%2C%20clear%2C%20and%20concise%20insights%20that%20not%20only%20inform%20but%20also%20empower%20your%20personal%20growth%20and%20broaden%20your%20perspective.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAcross%20all%20areas%20of%20our%20coverage%2C%20we'll%20shine%20a%20light%20on%20the%20rising%20stars%20and%20established%20changemakers%20making%20a%20genuine%20impact.%20We%20want%20to%20learn%20from%20them%20and%20know%20you%20do%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20course%2C%20even%20as%20we%20celebrate%20achievements%2C%20we'll%20hold%20those%20in%20power%20accountable.%20Like%20you%2C%20we%20believe%20the%20world%20should%20be%20more%20meritocratic%20and%20fair.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHere%20at%20Business%20Insider%2C%20we%20can't%20wait%20to%20share%20with%20you%20more%20stories%20that%20challenge%2C%20inspire%2C%20and%20drive%20progress%20%E2%80%94%20stories%20that%20resonate%20with%20your%20ambition%20and%20zest%20for%20life.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThank%20you%20for%20being%20a%20part%20of%20our%20community.%20Together%2C%20let's%20move%20forward%2C%20grow%20together%2C%20and%20shape%20a%20future%20that%20we%20all%20believe%20in.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWelcome%20to%20the%20new%20era%20of%20Business%20Insider.%20Let's%20make%20it%20extraordinary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fletter-from-business-insider-editor-nicholas-carlson-on-name-change-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22publis