a%3C%2Fem%3E%20(shameless)%E2%80%9D%20reacting%20to%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20comment%20that%20it%20was%20his%20%E2%80%9Cfoolishness%E2%80%9D%20that%20led%20him%20to%20get%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi%20to%20replace%20him%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20was%20addressing%20an%20election%20rally%20to%20seek%20votes%20for%20his%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20at%20Secunderabad%20in%20Telangana%20on%20November%2011%20when%20he%20reacted%20to%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20outburst%20in%20the%20Bihar%20assembly%20on%20November%209.%20%E2%80%9CNitish%20was%20in%20the%20habit%20of%20insulting%20the%20Dalits%20repeatedly%2C%E2%80%9D%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20known%20what%20political%20mileage%20the%20BJP%20would%20derive%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20upcoming%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Telangana%20by%20Modi%20calling%20Nitish%20a%20%E2%80%9Chabitual%20assaulter%E2%80%9D.%20Modi%20also%20described%20himself%20as%20a%20benefactor%20of%20the%20Dalits%2C%20claiming%20that%20he%20had%20stood%20with%20Chirag%20Paswan%2C%20son%20of%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Dalit%20leader%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%20%E2%80%9Cwhom%20Nitish%20insulted%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20the%20Bihar%20BJP%20leaders%20who%20were%20relatively%20subdued%20by%20the%20Bihar%20government%20raising%20the%20quota%20for%20the%20backward%20classes%20and%20the%20Dalits%20to%2065%25%20in%20the%20government%20jobs%2C%20followed%20up%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20comments%20to%20step%20up%20their%20attack%20on%20Nitish.%20The%20development%20has%20surprised%20the%20neutral%20observers%20%E2%80%93%20particularly%20the%20ones%2C%20who%20had%20closely%20watched%20the%20situation%20in%20which%20Nitish%20had%20%E2%80%98installed%E2%80%99%20Manjhi%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20owning%20responsibility%20for%20his%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%E2%80%99s%20poor%20performance%20in%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFew%20had%20imagined%20at%20that%20time%20that%20Nitish%20%E2%80%93%20the%20supreme%20leader%20of%20his%20party%20who%20had%20staged%20a%20comeback%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20after%20securing%20unprecedented%20victory%20for%20the%20JDU-BJP%20alliance%20with%20210%20seats%20in%20243%20member-Bihar%20assembly%20in%202010%20assembly%20polls%20%E2%80%93%20would%20demit%20his%20position%20in%20favour%20of%20someone%20else%20after%20the%20BJP%20had%20done%20well%20in%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20performed%20majestically%20in%20all%20the%20north%20Indian%20states%20in%202014%20and%20Bihar%20was%20not%20an%20exception.%20And%20it%20was%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20fought%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Modi%20against%20the%20Congress.%20In%20no%20way%2C%20Nitish%20could%20have%20been%20made%20accountable%20for%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20poor%20show%20in%20that%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06122347%2FF63GTNNWMAAsSYi.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06122347%2FF63GTNNWMAAsSYi.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06122347%2FF63GTNNWMAAsSYi-300x202.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06122347%2FF63GTNNWMAAsSYi-1024x688.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678572%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22806%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40narendramodi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20in%20Bihar%2C%20and%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20too%20had%20lost%20massively%20against%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20had%20projected%20Modi%20as%20the%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate%20and%20Modi%20had%20created%20waves%20in%20his%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2014%20scenario%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20on%20May%2020%2C%202014.%20The%20counting%20of%20votes%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20was%20over%20and%20preparations%20were%20afoot%20for%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20take%20over%20from%20Manmohan%20Singh%20as%20the%20prime%20minister%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Nitish%20Kumar%20called%20the%20meeting%20of%20his%20JD(U)%20legislature%20party%20and%20announced%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20own%20the%20moral%20responsibility%20of%20our%20party%E2%80%99s%20defeat%20at%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20and%20quit%20as%20your%20(JDU%E2%80%99s%20legislature%20party%E2%80%99s)%20leader.%20You%20are%20free%20to%20elect%20anyone%20from%20amongst%20you%20as%20your%20leader.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20about%2010%20am.%C2%A0%20All%20the%20JDU%20MLAs%20were%20stunned.%20They%20collectively%20objected%20to%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20decision%20and%20insisted%20on%20him%20not%20to%20do%20it.%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20senior%20from%20the%20JP%20movement%20days%20in%20the%201970s%20and%20then%20state%20JDU%20president%20Bashishtha%20Narayan%20Singh%20was%20miffed%20at%20Nitsh%E2%80%99s%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20then%20party%E2%80%99s%20national%20president%2C%20Sharad%20Yadav%2C%20landed%20in%20Patna%20at%20noon%2C%20driving%20to%20the%201-Aney%20Marg%20%E2%80%93%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20house%20and%20venue%20of%20the%20JDU%20legislature%20party%20meeting%20%E2%80%93%20to%20oversee%20the%20proceedings.%20The%20JDU%20cadres%20who%20had%20thronged%20in%20thousands%20outside%20the%201-Aney%20Marg%20hit%20out%20at%20Sharad%20Yadav%20when%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20hard%20to%20persuade%20Nitish%3B%20we%20will%20have%20to%20go%20by%20his%20decision.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20the%20president.%20It%E2%80%99s%20sacrilegious%20that%20you%20are%20unable%20to%20persuade%20Nitish%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Your%20conduct%20is%20not%20acceptable%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20cadre%20was%20heard%20blurting%20angrily%20at%20Sharad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MLAs%20kept%20up%20with%20their%20pressure%20on%20Nitish%20to%20withdraw%20his%20decision%20to%20quit%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20for%20almost%20five%20hours.%20However%2C%20they%20failed%20eventually%20and%20consented%20to%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20plan%20to%20nominate%20someone%20in%20his%20place.%20It%20was%20at%20about%202%3A30%20pm%20Nitish%20dropped%20the%20name%20of%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi%2C%20the%20MLA%20from%20Makhdumpur%20belonging%20to%20the%20Mahadalit%20Musahar%20community%2C%20as%20his%20replacement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReluctantly%2C%20the%20party%20MLAs%20acquiesced%20to%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20decision%20but%20they%20got%20the%20resolution%20passed%20that%20specifically%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CManjhi%20will%20remain%20CM%20only%20till%20the%20tenure%20of%20the%20present%20assembly%20(2010-2015).%20Nitish%20Kumar%20will%20lead%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20in%20the%202015%20assembly%20elections.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Foolish%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98stupid%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98orphan%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20interpreted%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20remark%20that%20his%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Emurkhata%3C%2Fem%3E%20(foolishness)%20led%20him%20to%20make%20Manjhi%20the%20CM%E2%80%9D%20as%20%E2%80%9Cshameless%20and%20humiliation%20to%20Manjhi%E2%80%9D%20which%20the%20Bihar%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20picked%20up%20to%20launch%20a%20frontal%20attack%20on%20Nitish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20fact%20remains%20that%20several%20JDU%20cadres%20were%20angry%20at%20Nitish%20for%20demitting%20office%20in%20Majhi%E2%80%99s%20favour.%20They%20weren%E2%80%99t%20ready%20to%20accept%20it.%20Outside%20the%201-Aney%20Marg%2C%20many%20JDU%20cadres%20were%20heard%20using%20the%20words%20like%20%E2%80%9Cfoolish%2C%20stupid%20and%20obstinate%E2%80%9D%20when%20they%20learnt%20about%20his%20decision%20to%20make%20Manjhi%20the%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20had%20emerged%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98hero%E2%80%99%20of%20the%C2%A0Mahadalits%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20bloc%20of%20the%20poor%20communities%20which%20he%20had%20given%20preferential%20treatment%20to%20in%20the%20jobs%2C%20panchayat%20raj%20bodies%20and%20a%20plethora%20of%20other%20welfare%20schemes.%20Manjhi%20was%20born%20and%20brought%20up%20in%20a%20Mahadalit%20community.%20But%20no%20Bihar%20leader%20had%20worked%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20Mahadalits%20in%20the%20manner%20Nitish%20had.%20Even%20the%20Mahadalit%20cadres%20of%20the%20JDU%20were%20pained%20at%20Nitish%20getting%20replaced%20with%20Manjhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20himself%20faced%20the%20cadres%E2%80%99%20angry%20outbursts%20when%20he%20escorted%20Manjhi%20to%20governor%20D.%20Y%20Patil%20and%20returned%20to%20stop%20at%20the%20gathering%20of%20the%20exasperated%20cadres%20with%20Manjhi%20by%20his%20side.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20made%20you%20the%20CM.%20Who%20has%20allowed%20you%20to%20subvert%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20mandate%20in%20favour%20of%20your%20personal%20choice%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20angry%20cadre%20shouted%20at%20him.%20Another%20screamed%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20made%20the%20people%20%3Cem%3Eanaath%3C%2Fem%3E%20(orphan)%20by%20relinquishing%20the%20responsibility%20given%20by%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14165552%2F1500x500.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14165552%2F1500x500.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14165552%2F1500x500-300x100.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14165552%2F1500x500-1024x341.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684733%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJitan%20Ram%20Manjhi%20swearing-in%20as%20chief%20minister%20of%20Bihar%20in%20May%202014.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%2F%40jitanrmanjhi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20cadres%20were%20heard%20using%20%E2%80%9Cfoolish%20and%20stupid%E2%80%9D%20words%20to%20describe%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20decision.%20Nitish%20pacified%20them%20by%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20will%20live%20with%20you%20and%20work%20according%20to%20your%20wishes%20and%20will.%20I%20will%20lead%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20again%20in%202015.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Nitish%20said%20that%20he%20made%20Manjhi%20the%20chief%20minister%20out%20of%20his%20%E2%80%9Cfoolishness%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20was%20merely%20repeating%20the%20words%20that%20his%20cadres%20had%20used%20against%20him%20on%20May%2020%2C%202014.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20the%20pre-Narendra%20Modi%20era%20media%20was%20sympathetic%20to%20Nitish.%20A%20few%20months%20before%20making%20Manjhi%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20Nitish%20vacated%20his%20chair%20for%20Dasrath%20Manjhi%20%E2%80%93%20a%20Mahadalit%20cultivator%20who%20had%20cut%20the%20rocks%20with%20the%20shovel%20and%20spade%20to%20make%20a%20path%20in%20the%20mountains%20of%20Gaya.%20The%20media%20had%20equated%20Manjhi%E2%80%99s%20installation%20with%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20symbolic%20gesture%20for%20Dasrath%20Manjhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManjhi%E2%80%99s%20U-turn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20making%20Manjhi%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20Nitish%20formed%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20with%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20and%20the%20Congress%20and%20fanned%20out%20in%20the%20north%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Champaran%20region%20to%20organise%20the%20electorate%20against%20the%20BJP.%20Jitan%20Manjhi%20stayed%20silent%20for%20a%20few%20weeks%20following%20up%20on%20the%20development%20work%20and%20welfare%20initiatives%20that%20Nitish%20had%20undertaken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20too%20embarked%20on%20the%20tours%20across%20the%20state%20causing%20embarrassing%20situations%20for%20Nitish%20by%20his%20%E2%80%98bizarre%E2%80%99%20conduct%20and%20utterances.%20At%20a%20public%20meeting%20at%20Darbhanga%2C%20he%20said%20that%20a%20temple%20was%20washed%20after%20he%20offered%20prayer%20in%20it%20and%20was%20found%20wrong%20by%20an%20inquiry%20committee.%20He%20described%20the%20upper%20castes%20as%20%E2%80%9Cforeigners%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20Dalits%20as%20%E2%80%9Caborigines%E2%80%9D%20and%20derided%20the%20lower%20caste%20women%20who%20had%20their%20husbands%20working%20in%20other%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbihar-jitan-ram-manjhi-exit-mahagathbandhan%5C%22%3EBihar%3A%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi%E2%80%99s%20Potential%20Exit%20Will%20Not%20Worry%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20JDU%20cadres%20were%20up%20in%20arms%20against%20Manjhi%20parading%20on%20the%20streets%20and%20demanding%20Nitish%20to%20replace%20him.%20But%20when%20the%202015%20assembly%20elections%20drew%20close%20and%20the%20party%20leadership%20demanded%20Majhi%20to%20demit%20the%20office%20in%20favour%20of%C2%A0%20Nitish%2C%20Manjhi%20rebelled%20levelling%20%E2%80%98insult%E2%80%99%20to%20him%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9Celitist%E2%80%9D%20JDU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20after%20a%20long%20and%20strenuous%20effort%20on%20the%20part%20of%20Sharad%20Yadav%2C%20Bashishtha%20Narayan%20Singh%2C%20and%20others%20in%20the%20party%2C%20Manjhi%20stepped%20down%20as%20the%20chief%20minister.%20But%2C%20after%20he%20stepped%20down%20as%20chief%20minister%2C%20Jitan%20Manjhi%20made%20his%20own%20party%20%E2%80%93%20Hindustani%20Awam%20Morcha%20(Secular)%20%E2%80%93%20that%20aligned%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%202015%20assembly%20elections%20against%20the%20Nitish-led%20JDU-RJD-Congress%20Mahagathbandhan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fnalin-verma%26source%3Dgmail-imap%26ust%3D1700462521000000%26usg%3DAOvVaw2-eWIxEMgG1CAj-Gsha6XF%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%253Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fnalin-verma%2526source%253Dgmail-imap%2526ust%253D1700462521000000%2526usg%253DAOvVaw2-eWIxEMgG1CAj-Gsha6XF%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1700030303126000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2L22b2ffNX8A-fCVH8EHgX%5C%22%3ENalin%C2%A0Verma%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20media%20educator%2C%20and%20independent%20researcher%20in%20folklore.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699964961000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14164628%2FThe-Wire-76.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-modis-counter-to-nitishs-outburst-at-jitan-ram-manjhi-doesnt-reveal-the-full-story%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Modi%20has%20recently%20called%20the%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20'shameless'%20after%20the%20latter%20said%20that%20it%20was%20his%20'foolishness'%20that%20led%20him%20to%20'install'%20Jitin%20Ram%20Manjhi%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20in%202014%20in%20his%20place.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-modis-counter-to-nitishs-outburst-at-jitan-ram-manjhi-doesnt-reveal-the-full-story%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Natco%20Pharma%20Q2%20results%3A%20Net%20profit%20surges%20over%206-fold%20to%20Rs%20369%20cr%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22pu