20corner%20of%20the%20country.%20One%20such%20community%20is%20the%20Chamar%20caste.%20According%20to%20the%20caste-based%20survey%20report%202022%20released%20by%20the%20Bihar%20government%2C%20there%20are%206%2C869%2C664%20people%20belonging%20to%20this%20caste%20in%20Bihar%2C%20which%20is%20about%205.255%20%25%20of%20the%20total%20population.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20political%20presence%20of%20the%20caste%20group%20has%20also%20been%20quite%20significant%20and%20it%20is%20no%20surprise%20that%20Jagjivan%20Ram%2C%20who%20hailed%20from%20this%20caste%20group%2C%20was%20at%20one%20point%20so%20influential%20that%20former%20prime%20minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20used%20to%20address%20him%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBabu%20ji%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20In%201977%2C%20when%20a%20non-Congress%20government%20was%20formed%2C%20he%20was%20made%20the%20deputy%20Prime%20Minister.%20In%20Bihar%20itself%2C%20a%20place%20where%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20castes%20have%20remained%20dominant%2C%20Ramsundar%20Das%2C%20of%20the%20community%2C%20was%20chief%20minister%20from%20April%2021%2C%201979%20to%20February%2017%2C%201980.%20Notably%2C%20this%20was%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Kanshi%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20Bahujan%20movement%20had%20not%20yet%20reached%20Bihar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20346px)%2085vw%2C%20346px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22346%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%20838w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-210x300.jpg%20210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%20715w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22496%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20there%20is%20a%20huge%20difference%20between%20political%20and%20social%20consciousness.%20To%20understand%20why%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Chamar%20caste%20group%20are%20mistreated%20even%20today%2C%20there%20is%20need%20for%20deep%20sociological%20reflection.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20development%20of%20human%20civilisation%20is%20a%20continuous%20process.%20None%20of%20its%20phases%20were%20completed%20immediately%20after%20they%20began.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20their%20course%20of%20development%2C%20humans%20adopted%20farming%20after%20hunting%20which%20was%20a%20great%20achievement%20for%20the%20human%20race%20ever%20since%20its%20origin.%20But%20since%20it%20was%20a%20collective%20achievement%2C%20it%20can%20be%20said%20that%20the%20primitive%20ancestors%20of%20all%20the%20people%20who%20have%20ever%20lived%20on%20this%20earth%20were%20farmers.%20In%20India%2C%20the%20remains%20of%20the%20Indus%20Valley%20civilisation%20indicate%20that%20agriculture%20was%20the%20most%20important%20activity.%20People%20carried%20out%20farming%20but%20they%20were%20also%20craftsmen%20who%20moulded%20urban%20civilisation%20in%20their%20own%20respective%20ways.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%20how%20were%20castes%20created%3F%20How%20did%20someone%20become%20a%20cobbler%20from%20a%20farmer%20when%20everybody%E2%80%99s%20main%20occupation%20was%20farming%3F%20This%20is%20a%20question%20which%20has%20not%20been%20discussed%20in%20academia%20enough.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChamars%20are%20historically%20a%20caste%20group%20which%20has%20maintained%20their%20hold%20on%20both%20farming%20and%20craftsmanship%20as%20occupations.%20In%20this%20regard%2C%20they%20are%20similar%20to%20carpenters%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebadhai)%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eor%20blacksmiths%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Elohar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E).%20Potters%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekumhar)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20can%20also%20be%20included%20in%20this%20category%3B%20they%20made%20utensils%2C%20pitchers%20and%20tiles%20from%20clay.%20Like%20all%20these%20crafts%2C%20the%20craft%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Echamar%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20cobbler%20is%20also%20fascinating.%20The%20people%20of%20this%20caste%20group%20ares%20also%20cattle%20herder%2C%20but%20they%20did%20not%20leave%20the%20corpses%20of%20dead%20animals%20to%20rot.%20They%20rendered%20even%20their%20mortal%20remains%20useful%20and%20it%20was%20owing%20to%20them%20that%20humans%20were%20able%20to%20protect%20themselves%20in%20the%20cold%20season%20by%20covering%20themselves%20with%20skins%20the%20Chamar%20people%20removed%20from%20dead%20animals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStrangely%2C%20the%20deity%20Shankar%20who%20is%20depicted%20as%20wearing%20the%20skin%20of%20a%20dead%20animal%20is%20worshiped%20by%20people%20of%20this%20country%20but%20the%20very%20people%20who%20have%20removed%20that%20skin%20from%20the%20animal%20and%20turned%20it%20into%20a%20piece%20of%20clothing%20for%20even%20the%20gods%20to%20adorn%20were%20deemed%20%E2%80%98untouchable%E2%80%99.%20Even%20today%2C%20this%20caste%20group%20is%20mistreated.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20one%20considers%20unrecorded%20history%2C%20the%20contribution%20of%20Chamars%20in%20farming%20has%20been%20no%20less%20than%20that%20of%20blacksmiths%20and%20carpenters.%20The%20people%20of%20the%20carpenter%20community%20made%20the%20wooden%20plough%2C%20and%20the%20blacksmiths%20smelted%20iron%20to%20make%20the%20plow%20which%20penetrates%20the%20ground%20and%20turns%20the%20soil.%20But%20none%20of%20this%20would%20be%20possible%20if%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Chamar%20caste%20had%20not%20made%20the%20leather%20bag%20which%20is%20used%20in%20the%20bellows%2C%20to%20collect%20air%20and%20thereby%20heat%20the%20coal%20of%20the%20furnace%20so%20that%20it%20melts%20even%20iron.%20It%20was%20an%20amazing%20invention%20about%20which%20nothing%20has%20been%20recorded%2C%20anywhere.%20The%20people%20of%20Chamar%20caste%20appear%20to%20have%20been%20the%20first%20to%20use%20valves.%20They%20learned%20from%20experience%20that%20there%20is%20no%20place%20in%20the%20world%20without%20air.%20Thus%20they%20made%20a%20big%20leather%20bag%20and%20fitted%20a%20valve%20in%20it%20so%20that%20when%20the%20bellow%20was%20lifted%2C%20air%20would%20rush%20in%20through%20the%20valve%20and%20when%20it%20was%20pressed%2C%20the%20valve%20would%20close%20and%20the%20air%20would%20come%20out%20through%20a%20fixed%20path%20and%20increase%20the%20temperature%20of%20the%20burning%20coal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20terms%20of%20public%20health%20as%20well%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Chamar%20caste%20have%20made%20a%20significant%20contribution%20by%20saving%20humanity%20from%20various%20epidemics.%20They%20carried%20the%20dead%20bodies%20of%20animals%20out%20of%20the%20village%20area%2C%20a%20practice%20which%20continues%20even%20today.%20Had%20they%20not%20been%20doing%20so%2C%20village%20after%20village%20would%20fall%20victim%20to%20various%20contagious%20diseases.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20caste%20system%20can%20be%20said%20to%20have%20destroyed%20the%20syncretic%20culture%20of%20India%20in%20which%20there%20was%20no%20distinction%20between%20blacksmiths%2C%20carpenters%2C%20potters%2C%20cobblers%20and%20other%20farmer%20groups.%20Whatever%20skill%20a%20person%20had%20was%20used%20and%20it%20laid%20the%20foundation%20of%20a%20developed%20society.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20most%20persecuted%20among%20the%20Dalits%20are%20people%20of%20the%20Chamar%20caste.%20Be%20it%20Rajasthan%20or%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20they%20are%20beaten%2C%20tortured%20and%20killed%20for%20trivial%20reasons%20like%20riding%20horses%20or%20donning%20a%20moustache.%20Even%20today%2C%20the%20stigma%20of%20untouchability%20is%20such%20that%20if%20they%20drink%20water%20from%20an%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20caste%20person%E2%80%99s%20pitcher%2C%20they%20are%20killed%20as%20punishment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20terms%20of%20political%20consciousness%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Chamar%20caste%20are%20enlightened.%20As%20a%20result%20no%20political%20party%20is%20in%20a%20position%20to%20ignore%20them%20today.%20People%20of%20this%20caste%20no%20longer%20support%20a%20party%20out%20of%20fear.%20Today%20they%20have%20their%20own%20ideology%20which%20was%20inspired%20by%20the%20ideology%20of%20Dr.%20B.R.%20Ambedkar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFamous%20mystic%20poet%20and%20saint%20Raidas%E2%80%99s%20message%20of%20breaking%20the%20caste%20barrier%20is%20an%20inspiration.%20Raidas%20was%20born%20in%20Kashi%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20but%20his%20message%20reached%20far%20and%20wide%2C%20including%20Bihar.%20The%20same%20Raidas%2C%20who%20had%20dreamed%20of%20Begumpura%20and%20had%20said%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSaid%20Raidas%20Khalas%20Chamara%2C%20the%20one%20who%20hails%20from%20that%20city%20is%20a%20friend%20of%20ours.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%20Read%20the%20Hindi%20original%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F260821%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-contributions-of-chamar-caste%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20earlier%20parts%20of%20the%20series%20on%20the%20following%20communities%20by%20clicking%20on%20their%20names%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-ghasi%5C%22%3EGhasi%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3E