%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHamas'%20armed%20wing%20said%20it%20was%20ready%20to%20free%2070%20Israeli%20hostages%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20five-day%20truce.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20said%20talks%20recently%20took%20place%20with%20Qatari%20mediators%2C%20who%20previously%20helped%20free%20four%20hostages.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERoughly%20240%20hostages%20were%20taken%20prisoner%20during%20Hamas'%20terrorist%20attack%20on%20Israel%20on%20October%207.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20armed%20wing%20of%20Hamas%20said%20on%20Monday%20it%20was%20ready%20to%20release%2070%20Israeli%20hostages%2C%20mainly%20women%20and%20children%2C%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20five-day%20truce%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbu%20Ubaida%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20for%20al-Qassam%20Brigades%2C%20said%20in%20an%20audio%20recording%20posted%20on%20Telegram%2C%20and%20reported%20on%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fhamas-armed-wing-discussed-releasing-70-hostages-return-5-day-truce-2023-11-13%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20negotiations%20have%20taken%20place%20with%20Qatari%20mediators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLast%20week%20there%20was%20an%20effort%20from%20the%20Qatari%20brothers%20to%20release%20the%20enemy%20captives%20from%20women%20and%20children%2C%20in%20return%20for%20the%20release%20of%20200%20Palestinian%20children%20and%2075%20women%20detained%20by%20the%20enemy%2C%26quot%3B%20Ubaida%20said%2C%20per%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20truce%2C%20according%20to%20Ubaida%2C%20%26quot%3Bshould%20include%20a%20complete%20cease-fire%20and%20allow%20aid%20and%20humanitarian%20relief%20everywhere%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%26quot%3B%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoughly%20240%20hostages%20were%20taken%20prisoner%20during%20Hamas'%20terrorist%20attack%20in%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%20which%20killed%20some%201%2C400%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20the%20militant%2