2071%2C%20has%20not%20declared%20whether%20he%20will%20run%2C%20saying%20he%20will%20announce%20that%20only%20after%20the%20parliament%20formally%20sets%20the%20election%20date.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fvladimir-putin-approves-new-restrictions-on-media-coverage-ahead-of-presidential-elections%2Farticleshow%2F105209424.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fvladimir-putin-approves-new-restrictions-on-media-coverage-ahead-of-presidential-elections%2Famp_articleshow%2F105209424.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fvladimir-putin-approves-new-restrictions-on-media-coverage-ahead-of-presidential-elections%2Famp_articleshow%2F105209424.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dogbite%20Victims%20To%20Get%2010%2C000%20For%20%26quot%3BEach%20Teeth%20Mark%26quot%3B%3A%20Big%20Court%20Order%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20judgment%20likely%20to%20set%20a%20precedent%20and%20spark%20a%20huge%20debate%2C%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court%20has%20said%20the%20State%20shall%20be%20%26quot%3Bprimarily%20responsible%26quot%3B%20to%20pay%20compensation%20in%20cases%20of%20attacks%20by%20stray%20animals%20such%20as%20dogs%20and%20cattle.%20In%20dog%20bite%20cases%2C%20it%20has%20said%2C%20the%20assistance%20shall%20be%20a%20minimum%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000%20%26quot%3Bper%20teeth%20mark%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20minimum%20of%20Rs%2020%2C000%20per%200.2%20cm%20of%20wound%20where%20the%20flesh%20has%20come%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20hearing%20a%20bunch%20of%20193%20petitions%20relating%20to%20attacks%20by%20stray%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20comes%20amid%20a%20huge%20debate%20in%20the%20country%20on%20the%20stray%20dog%20menace.%20The%20death%20of%2049-year-old%20Parag%20Desai%2C%20executive%20director%20with%20Wagh%20Bakri%20Tea%20Group%2C%20in%20October%20had%20sparked%20off%20a%20fresh%20round%20in%20the%20debate.%20A%20hospital%20statement%20had%20said%20Mr%20Desai%20died%20of%20a%20haemorrhage%20suffered%20in%20a%20fall%20after%20stray%20dogs%20chased%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20tragic%20incident%2C%20a%20section%20of%20social%20media%20users%20demanded%20urgent%20steps%20to%20tackle%20the%20stray%20dog%20problem%2C%20pointing%20to%20multiple%20cases%20of%20deaths%20and%20injuries%2C%20including%20to%20children%2C%20in%20animal%20attacks.%20Growing%20public%20anger%20over%20such%20cases%20has%20also%20led%20to%20incidents%20of%20animal%20cruelty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20State%20shall%20be%20primarily%20responsible%20to%20pay%20compensation%20with%C2%A0a%20right%20to%20recover%20the%20same%20from%20the%20defaulting%20Agencies%2F%20Instrumentalities%20of%20the%20State%20and%2For%20the%20private%20person%2C%20if%20any%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20High%20Court%20said%20in%20its%20order%20on%20a%20petition%20seeking%20compensation%20in%20a%20dogbite%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%20also%20asked%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%20and%20the%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Chandigarh%20to%20form%20a%20committee%20that%20will%20decide%20on%20compensation%20to%20be%20paid%20in%20cases%20of%20accidents%20caused%20or%20attacks%20by%20stray%20animals.%20These%20include%20animals%20such%20as%20cows%2C%20bulls%2C%20oxen%2C%20donkeys%2C%20dogs%2C%20nilgai%2C%20buffaloes%2C%20and%20wild%2C%20pet%20and%20deserted%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20said%20Committee%20shall%20be%20comprised%20of%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20the%20concerned%20District%20as%20its%20Chairperson%20and%20shall%20have%20the%20following%20member%20(a)%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2FDeputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(Traffic)%2C%20(b)%20Sub%20Divisional%20Magistrate%20of%20the%20concerned%20area%2C%20(c)%20The%20District%20Transport%20Officer%2C%20(d)%20Representative%20of%20the%20Chief%20Medical%20Officer%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judgment%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judgment%20is%20crucial%20considering%20the%20sensitive%20nature%20of%20the%20stray%20dog%20menace%2C%20an%20immensely%20polarising%20subject%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%202001%2C%20municipal%20authorities%20could%20euthanise%20stray%20dogs%20to%20keep%20public%20places%20safe.%20In%202001%20came%20the%20Animal%20Birth%20Control%20(Dogs)%20Rules.%20These%20rules%20created%20a%20separate%20category%20called%20%26quot%3Bstreet%20dogs%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20they%20should%20be%20sterilised%20and%20immunised%20by%20%26quot%3Bparticipation%20of%20animal%20welfare%20organizations%2C%20private%20individuals%20and%20the%20local%20authority%26quot%3B.%20Lack%20of%20adequate%20funds%20and%20manpower%20have%20frequently%20stalled%20such%20exercises%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20spike%20in%20stray%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202001%20rules%20were%20silent%20on%20euthanising%20stray%20dogs%20except%20those%20%26quot%3Bincurably%20ill%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bmortally%20wounded%26quot%3B.%20They%20also%20said%20dogs%20caught%20for%20sterlisation%20and%20vaccination%20should%20be%20%26quot%3Breleased%20in%20the%20same%20area%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699959840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Fe6u97c98_stray-dogs-generic_625x300_18_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F10-000-for-each-teeth-mark-courts-compensation-rate-in-dogbite-cases-4572858%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20judgment%20likely%20to%20set%20a%20precedent%20and%20spark%20a%20huge%20debate%2C%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court%20has%20said%20the%20State%20shall%20be%20%26quot%3Bprimarily%20responsible%26quot%3B%20to%20pay%20compensation%20in%20cases%20of%20attacks%20by%20stray%20animals%20such%20as%20dogs%20and%20cattle.%22%2C%22author%2