%2F105209203.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fred-cross-chief-to-meet-families-of-hostages-held-by-hamas%2Famp_articleshow%2F105209203.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fred-cross-chief-to-meet-families-of-hostages-held-by-hamas%2Famp_articleshow%2F105209203.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Women%20are%20turning%20to%20Facebook%20for%20a%20DIY%20approach%20to%20getting%20pregnant%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20holds%20a%20phone%20with%20the%20Facebook%20logo%20on%20the%20screen.%20Tiny%20white%20sperm%20cells%20swim%20towards%20the%20phone.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6552978858cf5fbccb95d24d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EArantza%20Pena%20Popo%2FInsider%3B%20iStock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20women%20have%20turned%20to%20Facebook%20groups%20to%20connect%20with%20free%20sperm%20donors%20and%20skirt%20sperm%20banks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESperm-bank%20prices%20have%20skyrocketed%20%E2%80%94%20a%20single%20vial%20of%20sperm%20can%20cost%20%241%2C000.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUnregulated%20sperm%20donation%20comes%20with%20plenty%20of%20risks%20but%20may%20be%20the%20only%20option%20for%20many%20women.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAngela%20spent%20two%20years%20trying%20to%20get%20pregnant%20through%20a%20sperm%20bank.%20But%20after%2010%20vials%20of%20donor%20sperm%2C%20she%20was%20out%20%2410%2C000%20and%20still%20didn't%20have%20a%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20getting%20too%20expensive%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20and%20her%20wife%20started%20considering%20other%20options.%20That's%20when%20a%20friend%20suggested%20Facebook%2C%20where%20groups%20dedicated%20to%20matching%20up%20donors%20and%20people%20who%20want%20to%20get%20pregnant%20have%20proliferated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAngela%2C%20whose%20last%20name%20has%20been%20removed%20to%20protect%20her%20privacy%2C%20met%20Kyle%20Gordy%20in%20a%20group%20called%20Sperm%20Donation%20USA.%20Gordy%20is%20a%20serial%20sperm%20donor%20%E2%80%94%20he%20says%20his%20donations%20have%20produced%2070%20children%20to%20date.%20He%20exchanged%20messages%20with%20Angela%20and%20her%20wife%20for%20about%20two%20weeks%20before%20the%20three%20decided%20to%20meet%20up%20in%20a%20public%20parking%20lot%2C%20where%20Kyle%20gave%20Angela%20a%20cup%20of%20his%20semen%20for%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20one%20of%20countless%20women%20who%20have%20sought%20out%20sperm%20donors%20on%20Facebook%2C%20much%20in%20the%20same%20way%20you%20might%20buy%20a%20used%20mattress%20or%20stationary%20bike.%20Many%20of%20these%20women%20can't%20afford%20sperm%20from%20a%20bank%2C%20where%20a%20single%20vial%20can%20cost%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fhealth%2Ffamily%2Fsperm-donor-cost%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%241%2C000%20or%20more%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Other%20fertility%20treatments%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fhealth%2Fwomens-health%2Fhow-much-does-ivf-cost%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eeven%20more%20expensive%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20they're%20not%20typically%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fivf-fertility-health-insurance-2052f7a172a271c4e9c038721f28c883%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecovered%20by%20insurance%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20pushing%20more%20people%20to%20take%20unregulated%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Edo-it-yourself%20approaches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAngela%20recalled%20that%20one%20of%20her%20friends%20said%20she%20spent%20roughly%20the%20equivalent%20of%20a%20down%20payment%20on%20a%20house%20in%20fertility%20treatments%20to%20get%20pregnant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20for%20these%20people%20who%20have%20to%20spend%20all%20this%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20supposed%20to%20be%20saving%20that%20for%20having%20kids.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22health%20parenting%20kids%20family%20children%20regression%20toys%20autism%20disability%20pregnancy%20stick%20test%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5ecd3065f0f41901f405210d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECrystal%20Cox%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinding%20free%20donors%20online%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20largely%20doesn't%20track%20sperm-bank%20data%2C%20from%20how%20many%20men%20donate%20to%20banks%20to%20how%20many%20children%20are%20conceived%20via%20sperm%20donation%20every%20year.%20So%20while%20US%20sperm-bank%20costs%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fsperm-donor-cost-pregnant-babies-fde53e2f%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewidely%20recognized%20to%20be%20increasing%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20no%20data%20has%20been%20collected%20on%20the%20extent%20of%20those%20increases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20reason%20for%20the%20increases%20may%20be%20that%20banks%20are%20now%20screening%20for%20many%20more%20genetic%20conditions%20in%20their%20donors%20than%20ever%20before%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eleaving%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usnews.com%2Fnews%2Fhealth-news%2Farticles%2F2023-01-10%2Fjust-4-of-men-who-apply-as-sperm-donors-are-accepted%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eshortage%20of%20men%20eligible%20to%20donate%20to%20sperm%20banks%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20seem%20to%20be%20transferring%20some%20of%20the%20testing%20costs%20onto%20the%20patients%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20patients%20want%20more%20thoroughly%20tested%20gametes%2C%20there's%20going%20to%20be%20an%20added%20expense%20for%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Sean%20Tipton%2C%20the%20chief%20advocacy%2C%20policy%2C%20and%20development%20officer%20at%20the%20American%20Society%20for%20Reproductive%20Medicine%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKristina%20Graham%20first%20looked%20into%20buying%20sperm%20from%20a%20bank%20three%20years%20ago%20but%20found%20the%20options%20too%20pricey%2C%20especially%20if%20she%20ended%20up%20needing%20multiple%20tries%20to%20get%20pregnant.%20She%20said%20the%20lowest%20price%20she%20and%20her%20wife%20could%20find%20was%20%24500%20for%20one%20vial%20of%20sperm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20wife%20and%20I%20were%20thinking%2C%20'What%20if%20there%20were%20people%20who%20just%20wanted%20to%20do%20it%20for%20free%3F'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kristina%20Graham%2C%20right%2C%20and%20her%20wife.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65528c09385143459e8c35e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKristina%20Graham%2C%20right%2C%20and%20her%20wife.%3Cp%3EKristina%20Graham%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20since%20worked%20with%20two%20free%20sperm%20donors%20at%20different%20times%2C%20both%20of%20whom%20she%20met%20on%20Facebook.%20She's%20still%20trying%20to%20get%20pregnant%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20her%20current%20donor%20comes%20to%20her%20house%20when%20she's%20ovulating%20to%20ejaculate%20into%20a%20cup%20so%20Graham%20can%20use%20a%20syringe%20to%20insert%20the%20semen%20inside%20herself%20%E2%80%94%20a%20method%20called%20artificial%20insemination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWomen%20who%20work%20with%20free%20donors%20and%20choose%20artificial%20insemination%20can%20buy%20the%20materials%20they%20need%20online.%20Facebook%20groups%20suggest%20the%20use%20of%20soft%20cups%20for%20semen%20and%20lubricant%20launchers%20for%20the%20insemination.%20Companies%20such%20as%20Mosie%20Baby%20and%20Frida%20Fertility%20sell%20special%20at-home%20insemination%20kits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETraveling%20to%20donate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20sperm%20donors%20may%20be%20motivated%20by%20a%20desire%20to%20continue%20their%20genetic%20line%20or%20seek%20sexual%20contact%2C%20Graham%20said%20the%20donors%20she'd%20worked%20with%20just%20seemed%20to%20want%20to%20%26quot%3Bhelp%20make%20a%20family%20whole.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETyree%20Kelly%2C%20a%2032-year-old%20donor%20from%20Arizona%2C%20said%20he's%20atoning%20for%20sins%20he%20committed%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bbad%20adolescent.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20that%20I%20try%20and%20do%20to%20help%20as%20many%20people%20as%20possible%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20I'm%20helping%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22671%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tyree%20Kelly%2C%20a%20sperm%20donor%20from%20Arizona.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654ea6f63cc84b4dfa008943%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22678%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETyree%20Kelly%3Cp%3ETyree%20Kelly%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Kelly%20first%20considered%20donating%20his%20sperm%2C%20he%20looked%20into%20sperm%20banks%20but%20realized%20he%20wouldn't%20qualify%20because%20of%20his%20family's%20medical%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usatoday.com%2Fstory%2Fnews%2Fnation%2F2023%2F05%2F21%2Fblack-women-shortage-sperm-donors%2F70236194007%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBlack%20donors%20such%20as%20Kelly%20are%20particularly%20rare%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20sperm%20banks.%20Kelly%20said%20a%20lot%20of%20women%20on%20Facebook%20messaged%20him%20because%20they%20specifically%20wanted%20a%20Black%20donor%2C%20often%20because%20they%20or%20their%20partner%20is%20Black%20and%20they%20want%20their%20child%20to%20look%20like%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKelly%20has%20been%20a%20donor%20for%20five%20years%20and%20has%20worked%20with%20about%2045%20women.%20He%20said%20he%20traveled%20frequently%2C%20often%20multiple%20times%20a%20month%2C%20to%20meet%20with%20recipients.%20When%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20him%20in%20October%2C%20he%20had%20just%20flown%20to%20Maine%20to%20meet%20a%20recipient%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20donors%2C%20including%20Kelly%2C%20may%20ask%20women%20to%20cover%20expenses%20like%20gas%20or%20flights%20if%20they%20travel%20to%20donate.%20Donors%20can%20also%20mail%20their%20semen%20across%20the%20country%2C%20but%20that%2C%20too%2C%20can%20cost%20hundreds%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20syringe%20and%20cup%20from%20Mosie%20Baby's%20at-home%20insemination%20kit.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65528cf936d588dc55cf8681%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20syringe%20and%20cup%20from%20Mosie%20Baby's%20at-home%20insemination%20kit.%3Cp%3EMosie%20Baby%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20unregulated%20market%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20sperm%20banks%20in%20the%20US%20are%20subject%20to%20regulation%20by%20the%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%2C%20Facebook%20groups%20where%20people%20exchange%20free%20sperm%20lack%20oversight%2C%20posing%20risks%20for%20both%20recipients%20and%20donors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWomen%20may%20have%20to%20weed%20through%20some%20creeps%20when%20looking%20for%20a%20sperm%20donor%20on%20Facebook.%20Graham%20and%20Angela%20said%20they%20specified%20to%20prospective%20donors%20that%20they%20wanted%20to%20get%20pregnant%20only%20via%20artificial%20insemination.%20But%20at%20the%20last%20minute%2C%20some%20donors%20would%20say%20they%20wanted%20to%20do%20only%20natural%20insemination%20%E2%80%94%20in%20other%20words%2C%20intercourse%20%E2%80%94%20or%20that%20they%20needed%20to%20watch%20the%20insemination%20happen%2C%20Angela%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20one%20guy%20who%20said%2C%20I%20need%20to%20be%20in%20the%20room%20to%20see%20it%20was%20inserted%20into%20you%20and%20not%20your%20wife%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20like%2C%20we're%20absolutely%20not%20doing%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGraham%20recalled%20that%20one%20donor%20even%20asked%20her%20for%20a%20nude%20photo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20like%2C%20'I%20need%20to%20see%20who%20I'm%20getting%20pregnant%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPosts%20in%20the%20Facebook%20groups%20warn%20of%20scammers%20among%20both%20sperm%20donors%20and%20recipients%2C%20too.%20In%20some%20posts%2C%20women%20call%20out%20donors%20who've%20asked%20for%20money%20to%20ship%20their%20sperm%20across%20the%20country%2C%20only%20to%20take%20the%20payment%20and%20disappear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20scientist%20picks%20up%20a%20vial%20of%20frozen%20donor%20sperm.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6354020c390dfe00196d899b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20scientist%20picks%20up%20a%20vial%20of%20frozen%20donor%20sperm%20samples.%3Cp%3EWong%20Maye-E%2FAP%20Photo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20effort%20to%20minimize%20risk%2C%20some%20donors%20and%20intended%20parents%20sign%20contracts%2C%20which%20often%20delineate%20the%20role%20the%20donor%20should%20play%20in%20a%20future%20child's%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecipients%20may%20ask%20for%20a%20contract%20so%20the%20donor%20doesn't%20try%20to%20make%20a%20claim%20to%20the%20child%2C%20while%20donors%20may%20want%20to%20ensure%20they%20won't%20get%20roped%20into%20paying%20child%20support%20later%20on.%20However%2C%20some%20parts%20of%20these%20contracts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boydlawlosangeles.com%2Fdo-sperm-donors-pay-child-support%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Earen't%20enfor