0to%20supply%20ammunition%20to%20Ukraine%20in%20its%20war%20with%20Russia%2C%20according%20to%20a%20media%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20British%20military%20cargo%20plane%20flew%20from%20Pakistan%20Air%20Force%20Base%20Nur%20Khan%20in%20Rawalpindi%20to%20the%20British%20military%20base%20in%20Cyprus%2C%20Akrotiri%2C%20and%20then%20to%20Romania%20a%20total%20of%20five%20times%20to%20supply%20arms%20to%20the%20war-torn%20country%2C%20the%20BBC%20Urdu%20reported%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIslamabad%20has%2C%20however%2C%20consistently%20denied%20that%20it%20has%20provided%20any%20ammunition%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20a%20neighbouring%20country%20to%20Romania.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20details%20of%20the%20contract%20from%20the%20American%20Federal%20Procurement%20Data%20System%2C%20the%20BBC%20report%20claimed%20that%20Pakistan%20signed%20two%20contracts%20with%20American%20companies%20named%20%26quot%3BGlobal%20Military%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BNorthrop%20Grumman%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20sale%20of%20155mm%20shells.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20agreements%20to%20provide%20weapons%20to%20Ukraine%20were%20signed%20on%20August%2017%2C%202022%2C%20and%20were%20specifically%20linked%20to%20the%20purchase%20of%20155mm%20shells.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Foreign%20Office%20in%20Islamabad%20has%20denied%20any%20sale%20of%20arms%20and%20ammunition%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20saying%20that%20Pakistan%20maintained%20a%20policy%20of%20%26quot%3Bstrict%20neutrality%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20dispute%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20and%20did%20not%20provide%20them%20with%20any%20arms%20or%20ammunition%20in%20that%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20alleged%20agreements%20took%20place%20during%20the%20rule%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20Democratic%20Movement%20(PDM)%20-%20a%20multi-party%20coalition%20that%20ousted%20Imran%20Khan-led%20government%20through%20a%20no-trust%20vote%20in%20April%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20Pakistan%20Army%20chief%20Gen%20Qamar%20Javed%20Bajwa%2C%20who%20had%20pledged%20to%20take%20Pakistan-UK%20relations%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bnew%20height%26quot%3B%2C%20retired%20in%20November%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202022%2C%20when%20these%20alleged%20contracts%20were%20signed%2C%20the%20Ukraine%20crisis%20was%20very%20much%20a%20part%20of%20the%20political%20discourse%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20cricketer-turned-politician%20Khan's%20visit%20to%20Russia%20on%20February%2024%2C%20when%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20ordered%20an%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonths%20after%20the%20visit%2C%20Gen%20Bajwa%20publicly%20distanced%20from%20Mr%20Khan%20and%20called%20for%20the%20invasion%20to%20be%20stopped%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20visit%20to%20Pakistan%20this%20July%2C%20Ukrainian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Dmytro%20Kuleba%20also%20rejected%20reports%20that%20Pakistan%20was%20supplying%20arms%20to%20Ukraine%20to%20support%20its%20military%20during%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20with%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BBC%20Urdu%20report%20claimed%20that%20a%20USD%20232%20million%20contract%20was%20awarded%20to%20Global%20Military%20while%20another%20USD%20131%20million%20contract%20was%20signed%20with%20Northrop%20Grumman.%20%26quot%3BThese%20agreements%20expired%20last%20month%20i.e.%20October%202023%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20alleged%20that%20the%20deliveries%20were%20made%20in%20a%20British%20military%20cargo%20plane%20from%20the%20Nur%20Khan%20Air%20Base%2C%20which%20landed%20in%20Rawalpindi%20five%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20such%20plane%20landed%20in%20Rawalpindi%20in%20August%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEach%20time%2C%20the%20plane%20flew%20from%20Nur%20Khan%20Airbase%20to%20the%20British%20military%20base%20in%20Cyprus%20and%20then%20to%20Romania%2C%20that%20too%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Russia%20was%20waging%20war%20in%20Romania's%20neighbouring%20country%20Ukraine%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBBC%20Urdu%2C%20while%20citing%20further%20evidence%20for%20its%20claims%2C%20said%20data%20by%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20Pakistan%20also%20showed%20that%20the%20country's%20arms%20exports%20increased%20by%203%2C000%20per%20cent%20during%20FY%202022-23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPakistan%20exported%20arms%20worth%20USD%2013%20million%20in%202021-22%2C%20while%20these%20exports%20reached%20USD%20415%20million%20in%202022-23%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20reports%20said%20secret%20Pakistani%20arms%20sales%20to%20the%20US%20to%20be%20used%20by%20Ukraine%20helped%20cash-strapped%20Islamabad%20secure%20a%20crucial%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20(IMF)%20bailout%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arms%20sales%20were%20made%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20supplying%20the%20Ukrainian%20military%20-%20marking%20Pakistani%20involvement%20in%20a%20conflict%20it%20had%20faced%20US%20pressure%20to%20take%20sides%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20Foreign%20Office%20Spokesperson%20Mumtaz%20Zahra%20Baloch%2C%20however%2C%20rejected%20as%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%20and%20fabricated%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20which%20says%20the%20cash-strapped%20country%20provided%20arms%20to%20the%20US%20to%20get%20its%20support%20to%20clinch%20the%20USD%203%20billion%20deal%20with%20the%20IMF%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20June%20to%20avoid%20default.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699958940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-03%2Ffehrru2o_pakistan-flag-reuters_650x400_07_March_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcash-strapped-pakistan-sold-weapons-worth-364-million-to-ukraine-report-4573129%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cash-strapped%20Pakistan%20repor