Twitter)%2C%20shows%20the%20former%20adult%20star%20voicing%20the%20controversial%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shared%20the%20clip%20in%20response%20to%20a%20post%20from%20comedian%20Marcella%20Arguello%2C%20who%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BWho%20else%20remembers%20being%20against%20the%20Iraq%20war%20and%20people%20being%20like%20oh%20wow%20so%20you%20don't%20SUPPORT%20OUR%20TROOPS%3F!%3F!%20And%20then%20having%20the%20most%20dumb%20conversation%20about%20being%20anti%20American%20when%20you%20were%20just%20anti%20killing%20innocent%20people.%20Anyway%20this%20feels%20like%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20being%20shared%2C%20Ms%20Khalifa's%20post%20has%20amassed%20a%20million%20views%20and%20over%20seven%20thousand%20likes.%20But%20Ms%20Khalifa%20most%20of%20the%20users%20have%20criticised%20Ms%20Khalifa%20for%20the%20bizarre%20comparison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSays%20the%20woman%20who%20is%20allowed%20to%20expose%20herself%20for%20cash%20based%20on%20the%20freedoms%20provided%20by%20our%20service%20members.%20You've%20never%20sacrificed%20a%20thing%20for%20anyone%20other%20than%20yourself.%20You%20are%20a%20sad%20excuse%20for%20a%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20commented%20a%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20second%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20so%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BBoth%20are%20terrible.%20However%20one%20is%20way%20more%20respectable.%20Soldiers%20give%20up%20their%20human%20rights%20so%20you%20can%20have%20yours%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20takes%20you%20serious%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20another%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20selling%20your%20body%20in%20the%20army%20for%20a%20Country%20you%20believe%20in.%20This%20makes%20ZERO%20sense.%20You%20are%20%26quot%3Bsacraficing%26quot%3B%20and%20offering%20your%20ABILITIES%20to%20a%20Country%20that%20you%20want%20to%20defend.%20Not%20sure%20what%20you%20are%20defending%20on%20Onlyfans%20with%20your%20body%20or%20human%20Abli