9%2C%20Now%2036%20Left%26quot%3B%2C%20Says%20Doctor%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seven%20are%20among%2039%20born%20prematurely%20-%20they%20weigh%20less%20than%201.5%20kg%20each.%20Each%20should%20be%20in%20incubators%20so%20body%20temperatures%20can%20be%20regulated.%20Instead%2C%20they%20were%20moved%20to%20ordinary%20beds%20-%20placed%20side-by-side%20and%20covered%20by%20packets%20of%20nappies%20and%20cardboard%20boxes%20of%20sterile%20gauze%20-%20over%20the%20weekend%20because%20there%20is%20no%20more%20fuel%20to%20run%20the%20generators%20that%20power%20the%20incubators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYesterday%20I%20had%2039%20babies...%20today%2036%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Mohamed%20Tabasha%2C%20the%20paediatric%20head%2C%20told%20Reuters%20Monday.%20%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20say%20how%20long%20they%20can%20last.%20I%20can%20lose%20another%20two%20babies%20today...%20or%20in%20an%20hour.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20three%20more%20(and%20nine%20adult%20patients)%20had%20died%2C%20AFP%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20health%20ministry%20in%20Hamas-run%20Gaza%20says%20the%20assault%20has%20already%20killed%2011%2C240%20people%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20are%20civilians%20and%20at%20least%2040%20per%20cent%20of%20whom%20were%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20vowed%20%26quot%3Bvengeance%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20Hamas'%20October%207%20terror%20attack%20that%20killed%20over%201%2C200%2C%20including%20children%2C%20but%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20is%20coming%20under%20growing%20international%20pressure%20-%20after%20many%20Western%20nations%20first%20refused%20to%20openly%20criticise%20Tel%20Aviv%20for%20its%20brutal%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20face%20of%20that%20pressure%2C%20Israel%20has%20agreed%20to%20daily%20pauses%20in%20military%20operations%20around%20specified%20humanitarian%20%26quot%3Bcorridors%26quot%3B%20to%20allow%20civilians%20to%20flee%20fighting.%20However%2C%20Israel%20has