0blind%20spot%20detection%2C%20door%20open%20alert%2C%20traffic%20sign%20recognition%2C%20rear%20cross-traffic%20alert%20and%20rear%20collision%20warning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%3A%20A%20Blueprint%20with%20Immediate%20and%20Long-Term%20Measures%20to%20Contain%20Violence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04223216%2Fimage-968.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fmanipur-has-achieved-90-per-cent-peace-chief-minister-biren-singh-2451136-2023-10-19%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Manipur%20that%20the%20violence%20in%20the%20state%20is%2090%25%20under%20control%20is%20shocking%20given%20the%20fact%20that%20almost%20six%20months%20of%20ethnic%20violence%20there%20remains%20unabated%20and%20keeps%20flaring%20up%20sporadically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20far%20worse%20than%20even%20what%20prevailed%20during%20the%20partition.%20Even%20at%20the%20height%20of%20ethnic%20cleansing%20during%20that%20time%2C%20there%20still%20remained%20and%20continue%20to%20exist%20several%20pockets%20where%20minority%20communities%20continued%20to%20live%20peacefully%20within%20the%20majority-dominated%20areas.%20Malerkotla%20in%20Punjab%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnuh-riots-fact-finding-team-persecution-of-muslims%5C%22%3ENuh%3C%2Fa%3E%20(notwithstanding%20the%20recent%20aberration%20caused%20by%20some%20troublemakers%20from%20outside)%20in%20Haryana%20are%20such%20examples%20of%20peace%20and%20harmony.%20Similar%20islands%20of%20Hindu%20minorities%20exist%20in%20Sindh%20province%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20many%20areas%20in%20Bangladesh.%20The%20situation%20is%20entirely%20different%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ethnic%20divide%20between%20the%20Kuki%20and%20Meitei%20people%20in%20Manipur%20is%20complete.%20Being%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20violence%2C%20there%20are%20no%20more%20Kukis%20left%20in%20the%20Valley%20dominated%20by%20Meiteis%20and%20similarly%20no%20Meiteis%20remain%20in%20hill%20areas%20dominated%20by%20Kukis.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20establishment%20has%20been%20compelled%20to%20separate%20Kuki%20and%20Meitei%20communities%20from%20each%20other%20by%20way%20of%20creating%20buffer%20zones%20and%20deploying%20security%20forces%20along%20these%20buffer%20zones%20to%20regulate%20entry%20and%20exit%20in%20a%20manner%20similar%20to%20what%20happens%20on%20an%20international%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-violence-reasons-failure-and-solution-q-and-a%5C%22%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20Behind%20the%20Manipur%20Violence%20and%20Why%20Stopping%20It%20Poses%20a%20Test%20For%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20automatic%20weapons%2C%20including%20rocket%20launchers%20and%20lakhs%20of%20ammunition%2C%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsurrender-illegal-weapons-in-15-days-or-face-action-manipur-cm-warns-people%5C%22%3Elooted%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20police%20and%20India%20Reserve%20Battalion%20(IRB)%20armouries.%20These%20are%20being%20used%20by%20perpetrators%20of%20violence%20with%20impunity%20in%20targeting%20civilians.%20The%20state%20government%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20meekly%20requesting%20the%20looters%20to%20return%20these%20weapons%20and%20ammunition%20without%20any%20result.%20Over%20200%20lives%20have%20been%20lost%20and%20more%20than%2075%2C000%20persons%20have%20been%20internally%20displaced.%20However%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20action%20on%20the%20part%20of%20both%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20governments%20(ruled%20by%20the%20BJP)%20is%20inexplicable.%20This%20inaction%20has%20angered%20the%20public%20against%20both%20the%20state%20and%20Union%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20unit%20of%20BJP%20is%20reported%20to%20have%20stated%20this%20in%20unequivocal%20terms%20in%20a%20letter%20written%20to%20the%20center%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6.%20public%20anger%20and%20protests%20are%20slowly%20turning%20the%20tide%2C%20placing%20the%20responsibility%20of%20this%20prolonged%20disturbance%20squarely%20on%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20address%20the%20situation%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%20The%20chief%20minister%20who%20is%20a%20Meitei%20himself%20appears%20to%20be%20fast%20losing%20support%20within%20his%20own%20community%20with%20his%20house%20and%20the%20house%20of%20the%20state%20BJP%20chief%20being%20attacked%20by%20Meitei%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22095913%2FF6ga_ibawAAlDWp.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22095913%2FF6ga_ibawAAlDWp.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22095913%2FF6ga_ibawAAlDWp-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22095913%2FF6ga_ibawAAlDWp-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-674218%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image%20of%20a%20Manipur%20Police%20checkpoint.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40manipur_police%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20sad%20reflection%20on%20the%20incompetence%20of%20institutions%20of%20state%20if%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20population%20has%20no%20faith%20in%20state%20police%20and%20are%20compelled%20to%20raise%20and%20depend%20on%20Village%20Defence%20Committees%20to%20ensure%20their%20own%20safety%20and%20security%20from%20people%20of%20other%20community.%20The%20incompetence%20of%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20has%20been%20proved%20beyond%20doubt%20by%20its%20abject%20surrender%20to%20mobs%20who%20looted%20their%20armouries.%20People%20do%20not%20trust%20it%20to%20provide%20security%20to%20them.%20Not%20only%20the%20police%2C%20the%20bureaucracy%20as%20well%20as%20state%20government%20have%20proved%20themselves%20to%20be%20totally%20incompetent.%20People%20have%20lost%20confidence%20in%20the%20institutions%20of%20the%20state.%20The%20writ%20of%20the%20state%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20appear%20to%20run%20any%20longer%20in%20Manipur%20and%20it%20is%20fully%20and%20truly%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20civil%20war.%20The%20situation%20if%20not%20controlled%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20portend%20well%20for%20the%20peace%20and%20stability%20of%20the%20entire%20North%20East%20India%2C%20large%20parts%20of%20which%20were%20in%20turmoil%20till%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20spite%20of%20the%20situation%20being%20so%20serious%20and%20its%20ramifications%20for%20the%20future%20of%20the%20Northeast%2C%20the%20policy%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20continues%20to%20remain%20in%20drift.%20It%20is%20surprising%20to%20note%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20continues%20to%20repose%20faith%20in%20Biren%20Singh%20in%20spite%20of%20violence.%20The%20statement%20by%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20that%20chief%20minister%20has%20not%20been%20removed%20because%20%E2%80%9Che%20is%20cooperating%E2%80%9D%20is%20bewildering%20because%20the%20decision%20about%20the%20imposition%20of%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20rule%20has%20to%20be%20based%20on%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20state.%20It%20is%20irrefutable%20that%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20has%20broken%20irrevocably%20and%20the%20imposition%20of%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20rule%20would%20have%20been%20a%20logical%20step%20to%20restore%20normalcy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20Manipur%20Police%20and%20Assam%20Rifles%20deployed%20to%20control%20the%20violence%20are%20not%20trusted%20by%20one%20or%20the%20other%20parties%20in%20conflict%20makes%20the%20case%20for%20imposition%20of%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20rule%20even%20stronger.%20Decisions%20like%20leaving%20out%2019%20police%20stations%20located%20in%20the%20valley%20%E2%80%93%20dominated%20by%20the%20Meitei%20community%20%E2%80%93%20while%20extending%20AFSPA%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20state%20or%20scrapping%20of%20%E2%80%9Csuspension%20of%20operations%E2%80%9D%20agreement%20only%20with%20Kuki%20insurgent%20groups%20are%20astonishing%20and%20smack%20of%20partisan%20state%20leadership.%20The%20Meitei%20insurgent%20groups%2C%20however%2C%20not%20only%20continue%20to%20remain%20armed%2C%20they%20have%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20added%20to%20their%20inventory%20with%20most%20of%20the%20arms%20looted%20from%20police%20having%20gone%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fland-narcotics-trade-and-local-power-dynamics-the-underlying-factors-behind-manipur-chaos%5C%22%3E143%20Days%20for%20Manipur%20Mayhem%3A%20The%20Centre%20Must%20At%20Least%20Give%20Biren%20Singh%20Marching%20Orders%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20status%20of%20imposition%20of%20Article%20355%20remains%20shrouded%20in%20mystery%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20retired%20IPS%20officer%20has%20been%20appointed%20to%20oversee%20the%20functioning%20of%20Manipur%20Police%20purportedly%20under%20provisions%20of%20this%20article.%20However%2C%20no%20notification%20regarding%20the%20imposition%20of%20355%20is%20available%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20In%20a%20reported%20response%20to%20an%20RTI%20query%2C%20MHA%20was%20not%20able%20to%20provide%20any%20clarity%20on%20this%20issue%20by%20stating%20that%20they%20do%20not%20have%20any%20information%20on%20the%20imposition%20of%20Article%20355.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%20appointed%20for%20such%20oversight%20is%20supposed%20to%20report%20directly%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20order%20to%20obviate%20any%20interference%20by%20the%20state%20government.%20However%2C%20being%20an%20outsider%2C%20this%20officer%20probably%20does%20not%20have%20any%20control%20over%20the%20day-to-day%20functioning%20of%20Manipur%20Police%2C%20which%20is%20deeply%20divided%20along%20ethnic%20lines.%20Police%2C%20the%20main%20agency%20responsible%20for%20controlling%20the%20situation%2C%20are%20acting%20in%20a%20partisan%20manner.%20The%20situation%20is%20so%20bad%20that%20police%20personnel%20belonging%20to%20one%20community%20cannot%20go%20to%20patrol%20the%20area%20where%20the%20other%20community%20is%20dominant.%20The%20Peace%20Committees%20set%20up%20in%20June%20have%20achieved%20no%20success%20and%20violence%20continues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20resolution%20of%20the%20conflict%20is%20extremely%20important%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20secessionist%20insurgency%20in%20the%20North%20East%20isn%E2%80%99t%20revived.%20The%20burning%20of%20over%20two%20hundred%20churches%20and%20almost%20two%20dozen%20temples%20may%20also%20be%20exploited%20by%20communal%20elements%20by%20giving%20it%20a%20colour%20of%20the%20Hindu-Christian%20conflict.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Mizoram%20in%20a%20recent%20interview%20to%20a%20prominent%20media%20group%20has%20alluded%20to%20the%20communal%20nature%20of%20the%20problem.%20With%20inimical%20neighbours%20like%20China%20ever%20ready%20to%20fish%20in%20troubled%20waters%2C%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20nation%20is%20at%20stake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspicion%20amongst%20communities%20is%20so%20deep-rooted%20that%20bringing%20normalcy%20will%20be%20a%20long-drawn%20affair.%20However%2C%20a%20start%20has%20to%20be%20made%20and%20the%20first%20step%20in%20that%20direction%20must%20be%20to%20contain%20widespread%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriority%20therefore%20must%20be%20to%20restore%20peace%20at%20the%20earliest.%20Imposition%20of%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%20in%20the%20early%20stages%20itself%20would%20have%20gone%20a%20long%20way%20in%20controlling%20the%20violence%20through%20the%20deployment%20of%20centrally%20controlled%20and%20impartial%20Central%20Armed%20Forces%2C%20like%20CRPF%2C%20BSF%2C%20ITBP%2C%20SSB%2C%20etc.%2C%20besides%20the%20Indian%20Army.%20Imposition%20of%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20rule%20and%20deployment%20of%20these%20forces%20even%20at%20this%20stage%20will%20infuse%20confidence%20amongst%20people%20as%20these%20forces%20are%20unconcerned%20with%20local%20ethnic%20loyalties.%20This%20cannot%20be%20said%20of%20Manipur%20Police%20which%20is%20accused%20of%20openly%20siding%20with%20the%20Meitei%20community.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Assam%20Rifles%20is%20accused%20of%20being%20partial%20towards%20Kukis%20by%20Meiteis.%20The%20imposition%20of%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20rule%20will%20also%20remove%20the%20Biren%20Singh%20Ministry%20%E2%80%93%20which%20has%20lost%20legitimacy%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20all%20communities%20%E2%80%93%20and%20create%20confidence%20amongst%20the%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20important%20that%20the%20weapons%20looted%20by%20miscreants%20must%20return%20to%20the%20armouries.%20The%20armed%20forces%20will%20have%20to%20conduct%20aggressive%20operations%20to%20recover%20these.%20This%20is%20possible%20only%20by%20delegating%20adequate%20powers%20to%20them%20through%20the%20imposition%20of%20AFSPA%20in%20the%20entire%20state%20including%2019%20police%20stations%20in%20the%20Manipur%20valley%20left%20out%20of%20its%20ambit%20so%20far.%20Delegation%20of%20such%20powers%20to%20Central%20Armed%20Forces%20will%20enable%20them%20to%20operate%20freely%20and%20conduct%20searches%20and%20combing%20operations%20to%20recover%20the%20looted%20weapons%20besides%20enabling%20them%20to%20apprehend%20insurgents%2C%20extortionists%2C%20and%20criminals%20indulging%20in%20violence%20and%20stop%20indiscriminate%20killings%20and%20help%20establish%20the%20Rule%20of%20Law.%20Special%20investigating%20teams%20and%20fast-track%20courts%20should%20also%20be%20considered%20to%20investigate%20and%20bring%20the%20culprits%20to%20trial%20at%20the%20earliest.%20Bringing%20perpetrators%20of%20violence%2C%20and%20those%20who%20have%20committed%20heinous%20crimes%2C%20especially%20against%20women%20and%20children%20to%20justice%20is%20the%20only%20way%20of%20bringing%20closure%20for%20the%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19203619%2FFyQ9vBxaIAAY1u3.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19203619%2FFyQ9vBxaIAAY1u3.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19203619%2FFyQ9vBxaIAAY1u3-300x221.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19203619%2FFyQ9vBxaIAAY1u3-1024x754.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-659022%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22884%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGun%20drop%20box%20placed%20in%20Imphal%20Manipur.%20Authorities%20are%20asking%20people%20to%20voluntarily%20return%20snatched%20and%20looted%20weapons.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20leaders%20and%20bureaucrats%20must%20increase%20their%20visibility%20in%20the%20trouble-prone%20area%20and%20visit%20them%20frequently%20to%20assess%20the%20situation%20firsthand%20and%20redress%20grievances%20of%20people%20on%20the%20spot%2C%20wherever%20possible%2C%20in%20order%20to%20restore%20the%20confidence%20of%20the%20masses%20in%20the%20establishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20peace%20committees%20need%20to%20act%20proactively%20and%20be%20innovative%20in%20their%20approach.%20People%20with%20impeccable%20integrity%20must%20be%20identified%20and%20incorporated%20into%20these%20committees.%20The%20community%20leaders%2C%20like%20village%20heads%20(known%20as%20%E2%80%9CGaon%20Budhas%E2%80%9D%20in%20those%20areas)%20who%20are%20well%20respected%20by%20communities%20in%20the%20North%20East%2C%20and%20prominent%20women%20organisations%20must%20be%20roped%20in%20to%20initiate%20dialogue%20amongst%20communities%20and%20remove%20suspicion%20and%20schism%20between%20communities.%20The%20realisation%20that%20the%20lives%20of%20different%20communities%20are%20inexorably%20interlinked%20and%20interdependent%20is%20the%20only%20way%20to%20contain%20the%20violence.%20Naga%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20who%20have%20continued%20to%20remain%20neutral%20%E2%80%93%20can%20be%20gainfully%20utilised%20to%20bring%20about%20a%20rapprochement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELong-term%20measures%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriority%20must%20be%20given%20to%20ensure%20effective%20Border%20Management%20of%20India%20%E2%80%93%20Myanmar%20Border%20to%20prevent%20illegal%20entrants%20from%20coming%20in%20and%20settling%20down%20in%20India%20which%20is%20said%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20main%20reasons%20for%20the%20strife%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20deployment%20of%20a%20border%20guarding%20force%20close%20to%20the%20border%20will%20also%20ensure%20the%20effective%20implementation%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CFree%20Movement%20Regime%E2%80%9D%20and%20proper%20maintenance%20of%20records%20of%20local%20tribals%20coming%20in%20and%20going%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeployment%20of%20Border%20Guarding%20Force%20and%20the%20consequent%20necessity%20to%20create%20infrastructure%20for%20providing%20logistics%20to%20troops%20deployed%20close%20to%20the%20border%20on%20BOPs%20will%20add%20to%20employment%20and%20therefore%20prosperity%20of%20the%20border%20population.%20Deployment%20of%20a%20force%20exclusively%20for%20Border%20Guarding%20will%20also%20release%20the%20entire%20Assam%20Rifles%20for%20dedicated%20deployment%20to%20control%20internal%20security%20problems%20in%20Manipur%20and%20other%20States%20of%20the%20North%20East%20which%20is%20the%20primary%20role%20of%20this%20elite%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20must%20also%20ensure%20that%20remote%20areas%20of%20the%20state%20are%20provided%20with%20good%20administration%20and%20that%20the%20fruits%20of%20development%20reach%20the%20Hill%20communities.%20One%20of%20the%20major%20grievances%20%E2%80%93%20and%20true%20to%20a%20large%20extent%20%E2%80%93%20of%20Kukis%20is%20that%20most%20of%20the%20development%20has%20taken%20place%20in%20the%2010%25%20Valley%20area%20occupied%20by%20Meiteis.%20The%20remote%20hill%20areas%20must%20be%20developed%20and%20provided%20connectivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20own%20experience%20in%20Churachandpur%20in%20Manipur%20is%20that%20bureaucrats%20and%20police%20rarely%20if%20ever%20visit%20remote%20areas%20unless%2C%20of%20course%2C%20things%20have%20changed%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%20since%20I%20was%20there.%20The%20remote%20hill%20areas%20are%20still%20in%20a%20time-wrap%20with%20hardly%20any%20facilities%20and%20access%20to%20institutions%20and%20authorities%20to%20project%20their%20problems.%20As%20late%20as%202007%2C%20it%20took%20me%20over%20six%20hours%20to%20reach%20Behang%20%E2%80%93%20a%20border%20town%20along%20the%20India-Myanmar%20border%20from%20Churachandpur%20%E2%80%93%20a%20distance%20of%20only%20about%2070%20kilometres.%20My%20contacts%20informed%20me%20that%20there%20has%20been%20only%20a%20marginal%20improvement%20in%20the%20situation%20even%20after%2015%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20provided%20in%20Article%20371C%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20the%20Committee%20of%20the%20Legislative%20Assembly%20of%20the%20state%20consisting%20of%20members%20of%20the%20Manipur%20Assembly%20elected%20from%20the%20Hill%20Areas%20of%20the%20state%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20function%20effectively.%20Arrangements%20like%20Autonomous%20District%20Councils%20may%20also%20be%20considered%20in%20order%20to%20give%20more%20autonomy%20to%20Hill%20districts.%20Necessary%20financial%20grants%20should%20be%20made%20available%20to%20these%20councils%20to%20enable%20them%20to%20carry%20out%20developmental%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fbroad-consensus-in-manipur-that-state-responsible-for-ethnic-violence%5C%22%3EManipur%3A%20Both%20Centre%20and%20State%20Played%20a%20Principal%20Role%20in%20Ethnic%20Violence%2C%20Claims%20Fact-Finding%20Team%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Act%20East%20policy%20of%20India%2C%20which%20is%20aimed%20to%20enhance%20connectivity%2C%20trade%2C%20and%20improve%20relations%20with%20our%20Eastern%20neighbours%2C%20should%20be%20extended%20to%20include%20the%20development%20of%20North%20Eastern%20states%20and%20improve%20connectivity%20which%20is%20presently%20restricted%20only%20to%20main%20towns%20or%20capital%20cities%20of%20these%20states.%20Railway%20and%20Road%20networks%20are%20said%20to%20be%20the%20greatest%20integrators%20of%20communities.%20India%20must%20focus%20on%20ensuring%20connectivity%20to%20the%20remotest%20parts%20while%20at%20the%20same%20time%20ensuring%20that%20the%20fragile%20ecology%20of%20the%20area%20is%20not%20disturbed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20must%20enhance%20investment%20to%20improve%20the%20human%20development%20index.%20Focused%20investment%20in%20the%20education%20sector%2C%20environment-friendly%20industry%2C%20and%20agricultural%20activities%20in%20these%20states%20are%20essential.%20Investment%20in%20industry%20and%20infrastructure%20will%20lead%20to%20better%20avenues%20for%20employment%20and%20wean%20citizens%20away%20from%20indulging%20in%20violent%20criminal%20activities%20and%20drugs.%20The%20network%20of%20rail%20and%20roads%20in%20the%20remotest%20parts%20of%20these%20states%20is%20essential%20to%20integrate%20them%20with%20the%20main%20stream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllotting%20large%20tracts%20of%20land%20for%20something%20like%20Palm%20cultivation%20as%20widely%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.firstpost.com%2Findia%2Fwhy-centres-plan-to-expand-oil-palm-cultivation-across-north-east-worries-environmentalists-10030361.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20media%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20appear%20a%20viable%20option%20as%20it%20will%20adversely%20affect%20the%20biodiversity%20of%20the%20area.%20Planting%20palm%20oil%20trees%20harms%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20soil%2C%20depleting%20large%20amounts%20of%20nutrients%20from%20the%20soil%20thus%20degrading%20it.%20The%20resultant%20increase%20in%20use%20of%20herbicides%2C%20insecticides%2C%20and%20fertilisers%20contaminates%20water%20bodies%20and%20affects%20groundwater%20and%20the%20aquatic%20biodiversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20stop%20poppy%20cultivation%20in%20hill%20areas%20of%20Manipur%20through%20effective%20surveillance%20and%20deterrent%20action%20besides%20affirmative%20action%20by%20providing%20sustenance%20alternatives.%20People%20should%20be%20encouraged%20to%20take%20to%20poultry%20farming%2C%20dairy%20farming%2C%20and%20cattle%20rearing.%20The%20hill%20area%20having%20terrain%20and%20weather%20conditions%20similar%20to%20other%20areas%20of%20the%20Northeast%2C%20should%20be%20suitable%20for%20coffee%2C%20pineapple%2C%20orange%2C%20banana%2C%20and%20medicinal%20plantations%20or%20even%20rubber%20plantations.%20These%20cash%20crops%20will%20provide%20alternative%20means%20of%20income%20to%20hill%20people%20and%20thus%20decrease%20dependency%20on%20Poppy%20cultivation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04085450%2FFvO7YL1aEAAlR43.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04085450%2FFvO7YL1aEAAlR43.jpeg%201170w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04085450%2FFvO7YL1aEAAlR43-300x227.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04085450%2FFvO7YL1aEAAlR43-1024x775.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-651628%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22886%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFile%20photo%20of%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40MangteC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20of%20the%20inclusion%20of%20Meiteis%20in%20Schedule%20Tribe%20has%20to%20be%20deliberate%2C%20deeply%20after%20taking%20all%20factors%20into%20account.%20The%20authorities%20must%20consider%20recommendations%20made%20by%20various%20committees%20set%20up%20by%20the%20government%20from%20time%20to%20time%20in%20this%20regard.%20Assessment%20of%20five%20important%20criteria%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20Meitei%20community%20namely%2C%20primitive%20traits%2C%20distinct%20culture%2C%20geographical%20isolation%2C%20shyness%20of%20contact%20with%20the%20community%20at%20large%2C%20and%20backwardness%20recommended%20by%20the%20Lokur%20Committee%20in%201965%20will%20provide%20useful%20insights%20in%20determining%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recommendations%20of%20the%20Bhuria%20Commission%20(2002-04)%20which%20focused%20on%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20issues%20from%20the%20Fifth%20Schedule%20to%20tribal%20land%20and%20forest%2C%20health%20and%20education%2C%20working%20of%20Panchayats%2C%20and%20the%20status%20of%20tribal%20women%20to%20determine%20the%20Schedule%20Tribe%20status%20will%20also%20provide%20a%20benchmark%20to%20decide%20this%20vexed%20issue.%20Besides%20these%2C%20the%20recommendations%20made%20by%20the%20High-Level%20Committee%20(HLC)%20under%20the%20chairmanship%20of%20Prof%20Virginus%20Xaxa%20in%202013%20to%20study%20critical%20issues%20related%20to%20tribal%20communities%2C%20like%20livelihood%2C%20employment%2C%20education%2C%20health%2C%20involuntary%20displacement%2C%20and%20migration%20besides%20legal%20and%20constitutional%20matters%20must%20also%20be%20studied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20important%20point%20to%20consider%20is%20that%20the%20grant%20of%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20Status%20to%20Mieteis%20will%20deprive%20them%20of%20the%20benefit%20of%20SC%20and%20OBC%20reservations%20in%20government%20jobs.%20The%20model%20of%20reservations%20in%20government%20jobs%20adopted%20by%20Nagaland%20also%20should%20be%20studied.%20While%20all%2016%20Naga%20tribes%20are%20eligible%20for%20reservation%20as%20Schedule%20Tribes%20for%20Union%20government%20jobs%2C%20only%20eight%20most%20backward%20Naga%20tribes%20are%20eligible%20for%20reservation%20in%20state%20government%20jobs.%20However%2C%20the%20demand%20of%20Meiteis%20for%20Schedule%20Tribe%20Status%20is%20mainly%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20purchasing%20land%20in%20Hill%20areas%20not%20for%20reservation%20in%20government%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20important%20reason%20for%20strife%20in%20Manipur%20is%20the%20Land.%20The%20grouse%20of%20the%20Meitei%20people%20is%20that%20they%20are%20confined%20to%20just%20about%2011%25%20of%20the%20land%20area%20of%20the%20state%20in%20the%20valley%20being%20deprived%20of%20acquiring%20land%20in%20the%20hill%20areas%20because%20they%20do%20not%20have%20the%20status%20of%20Scheduled%20Tribes.%20The%20land%20in%20Manipur%20is%20regulated%20by%20two%20laws.%20First%2C%20The%20Manipur%20Land%20Revenue%20and%20Land%20Reforms%20Act%2C%201960%20(MLR%20%26amp%3B%20LR%20Act%2C%201960)%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20other%20pertaining%20to%20the%20regulation%20of%20land%20in%20Manipur%20is%20%E2%80%98The%20Manipur%20Conservation%20of%20Paddy%20Land%20and%20Wetland%20Act%2C%202014%20(Manipur%20Act%20No.%2010%20of%202014)%E2%80%99%20aims%20to%20conserve%20the%20paddy%20land%20and%20wetland%20and%20to%20restrict%20the%20conversion%20or%20reclamation%20thereof%20in%20order%20to%20promote%20growth%20in%20the%20agricultural%20sector%20in%20Manipur.%20T%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20Land%20Reform%20and%20Land%20Revenue%20Act%2C%201960%20is%20extended%20to%20the%20whole%20Valley%20along%20with%20a%20small%20portion%20of%20the%20hill%20area.%20The%20state%20government%20of%20Manipur%20has%20attempted%20on%20several%20occasions%20to%20make%20some%20amendments%20to%20MLR%20%26amp%3B%20LR%20including%20efforts%20to%20introduce%20the%20New%20Land%20Use%20Policy%2C%202014.%20Each%20such%20attempt%20has%20led%20to%20more%20conflict%20and%20polarisation%20in%20the%20state%20as%20these%20are%20considered%20to%20interfere%20with%20the%20tribal%20land%20ownership%20system%20based%20on%20traditional%20customary%20laws.%20These%20are%20considered%20attempts%20to%20marginalise%20the%20tribals%20and%20alienate%20them%20from%20ownership%20and%20possession%20of%20land.%20Tribal%20lands%20are%20privately%20owned%20by%20tribal%20individuals%20and%20remaining%20lands%20belong%20to%20whole%20community%20of%20respective%20village.%20In%20case%20of%20Kuki%20tribe%2C%20the%20village%20chief%20is%20generally%20accepted%20as%20the%20owner%20of%20all%20lands%20of%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%20158%20of%20the%20MLR%20and%20LR%20Act%20provides%20special%20provisions%20regarding%20Scheduled%20Tribes.%20This%20Section%20states%20that%20%E2%80%9CNo%20transfer%20of%20land%20by%20a%20person%20who%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20shall%20be%20valid%20unless%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%A6%20(b)%20where%20the%20transfer%20is%20to%20a%20person%20who%20is%20not%20a%20member%20of%20any%20such%20tribe%2C%20it%20is%20made%20with%20the%20previous%20permission%20in%20writing%20of%20the%20Deputy%20Commissioner%2C%20provided%20that%20the%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20shall%20not%20give%20such%20permission%20unless%20he%20has%20first%20secured%20the%20consent%20thereto%20of%20the%20District%20Council%20within%20whose%20jurisdiction%20the%20land%20lies%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D.%20However%2C%20since%20the%20MLR%20%26amp%3B%20LR%20act%20is%20not%20applicable%20to%20hill%20areas%2C%20this%20legal%20protection%20is%20theoretically%20not%20available%20to%20hill%20areas%20implying%20that%20non%20tribals%20can%20buy%20land%20in%20Tribal%20areas.%20Reportedly%2C%20there%20have%20been%20some%20such%20land%20transactions%20in%20the%20past.%20Under%20such%20circumstances%20the%20authorities%20need%20to%20take%20a%20close%20look%20at%20the%20entire%20gamut%20of%20Land%20laws%20and%20identify%20issues%20which%20need%20proper%20interpretation%20and%20implementation%20to%20the%20satisfaction%20of%20all%20ethnic%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContinued%20turmoil%20in%20Manipur%20is%20a%20serious%20threat%20to%20the%20security%20and%20integrity%20of%20India.%20In%20the%20worst-case%20scenario%2C%20it%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20turn%20into%20a%20secessionist%20insurgency%20or%20a%20festering%20communal%20problem%20at%20best%20(sic).%20Restoring%20normalcy%20at%20the%20earliest%20is%20most%20important.%20The%20situation%20therefore%20must%20be%20addressed%20with%20urgency%2C%20the%20first%20step%20towards%20which%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20violence%20is%20contained%20while%20at%20the%20same%20time%20simultaneously%20preparing%20ground%20for%20addressing%20issues%20having%20long-term%20implications%20as%20discussed%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20common%20saying%20goes%20%E2%80%9CRoof%20must%20be%20repaired%20when%20the%20sun%20is%20shining.%E2%80%9D%20It%20is%20still%20not%20too%20late%20and%20the%20authorities%20must%20rise%20above%20the%20parochial%20consideration%20of%20ethnicity%2C%20religion%2C%20and%20region%20to%20resolve%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESanjiv%20Krishan%20Sood%20retired%20as%20additional%20director%20general%20of%20the%20Border%20Security%20Force.%3C%