20inflation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20inflation%20rates%20are%20among%20the%20lowest%2C%20at%20four%20per%20cent%20or%20below.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhile%20the%20prices%20of%20fuel%20and%20light%20and%20edible%20oils%20dropped%20in%20October%2C%20there%20was%20a%20marginal%20increase%20in%20the%20prices%20of%20vegetables%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20transport%20and%20communications.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20The%20Economist%20published%20an%20article%20analyzing%20the%20inflation%20trend%20in%20developed%20countries.%20Their%20analysis%20indicates%20that%20inflation%20remains%20quite%20entrenched%2C%20even%20more%20so%20now%20than%20in%202022.%20The%20journal%20concludes%20that%20the%20situation%20continues%20to%20be%20challenging%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Canada%2C%20UK%2C%20and%20Australia%2C%20with%20some%20improvement%20seen%20in%20Italy%2C%20Spain%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20South%20Korea.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20India%20emerging%20as%20one%20of%20the%20bright%20spots%2C%20given%20the%20situation%20worldwide%3F%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGlobal%20investment%20bank%20major%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs%2C%20recently%20upgraded%20India's%20markets%20to%20overweight%20in%20an%20otherwise%20tricky%20period%20in%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20region.%20This%20follows%20earlier%20upgrades%20from%20institutions%20such%20as%20Morgan%20Stanley%2C%20CLSA%2C%20and%20Nomura.%20The%20factors%20driving%20these%20upgrades%20include%20macroeconomic%20stability%20in%20India%2C%20with%20a%20subdued%20inflation%20trajectory%20being%20one%20of%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699954980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2F5vjmr3qo_inflation_625x300_12_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finflation-drops-bjp-governments-outpace-rivals-among-poll-bound-states-4572967%22%2C%22summary%22