marked%20a%20significant%20win%20for%20Boeing%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20air%20show%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Fhub%2Fairlines%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eairlines%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0appear%20poised%20for%20even%20more%20billion-dollar%20deals%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmirates%20made%20the%20announcement%20witnessed%20by%20the%20crown%20prince%20of%20Dubai%2C%20Sheikh%20Hamad%20bin%20Mohammed%20Al%20Maktoum%2C%20at%20an%20afternoon%20news%20conference.%20Emirates%20CEO%20and%20Chairman%20Sheikh%20Ahmed%20bin%20Saeed%20Al%20Maktoum%20said%20the%20deal%20would%20see%20the%20carrier%20purchase%2090%20Boeing%20777%20aircraft%2C%2055%20of%20them%20777-9%20variants%20and%2035%20of%20them%20777-8s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmirates%20will%20also%20add%20five%20787%20Dreamliners%20to%20its%20previous%20order%20of%2030%20aircraft%2C%20Sheikh%20Saeed%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20777%20is%20at%20the%20center%20of%20Emirates'%20strategy%20to%20connect%20cities%20on%20all%20continents%20nonstop%20to%20Dubai.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStan%20Deal%2C%20an%20executive%20vice-president%20at%20Boeing%2C%20praised%20the%20deal%3A%20%26quot%3BAll%20these%20products%20point%20to%20the%20future%20of%20Emirates.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20order%20means%20Emirates%20now%20has%20205%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fmiddle-east-business-dubai-united-arab-emirates-f2421ad78d8275d8a1cea71c35957005%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoeing%20777%3C%2Fa%3E%20planes%20on%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmirates%20officials%20stressed%20that%20FlyDubai's%20order%20was%20separate%20from%20the%20long-haul%20carrier%2C%20though%20the%20two%20airlines%20are%20both%20owned%20by%20a%20sovereign%20wealth%20fund%20called%20the%20Investment%20Corporation%20of%20Dubai.%20The%20purchase%20represents%20a%20major%20change%20for%20FlyDubai%2C%20which%20to%20this%20point%20has%20on