20there%20were%20no%20salespeople%20there.%20A%20request%20for%20comment%20left%20with%20an%20attendant%20there%20was%20not%20immediately%20returned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERafael%20also%20sponsored%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fdubai-air-show-israel-palestinians-hamas-war-defense-industry-09f8fafac8434a5229e096613a738bc6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20meeting%20of%20air%20force%20commanders%20Sunday%20at%20a%20luxury%20Dubai%20hotel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20highlighting%20the%20balancing%20act%20being%20struck%20by%20the%20UAE%20amid%20anger%20in%20the%20Arab%20world%20over%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UAE%2C%20a%20federation%20of%20seven%20sheikhdoms%2C%20established%20diplomatic%20relations%20with%20Israel%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20Russian%20Helicopters%20had%20listed%20their%20staff%20would%20be%20on%20hand%20for%20the%20air%20show%20after%20appearing%20at%20the%20Abu%20Dhabi%20arms%20fair%20earlier%20this%20year%20despite%20being%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Frussia-ukraine-united-arab-emirates-government-abu-dhabi-business-912108195180fb5edf9dfb88fd6167b9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esanctioned%20by%20the%20U.S.%20and%20others%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0over%20Moscow's%20war%20on%20Ukraine.%20Roscosmos%2C%20the%20Russian%20state%20space%20company%2C%20is%20also%20at%20the%20show%2C%20as%20were%20the%20Russian%20Knights%2C%20the%20precision%20flying%20team%20of%20the%20Russian%20air%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Associated%20Press%20journalist%20at%20the%20show%20also%20saw%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Fhub%2Fkhalifa-hifter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGen.%20Khalifa%20Hifter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20leads%20the%20self-styled%20Libyan%20National%20Army%20and%20controls%20the%20North%20African%20nation's%20east%20and%20south.%20Another%20AP%20team%20saw%20Afgh