f-afghan-hindu-family-including-3-children-killed-in-london-house-fire-on-diwali-night-4572857%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fseema-ratra-hounslow-fire-5-of-afghan-hindu-family-including-3-children-killed-in-london-house-fire-on-diwali-night-4572857%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fseema-ratra-hounslow-fire-5-of-afghan-hindu-family-including-3-children-killed-in-london-house-fire-on-diwali-night-4572857%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Respect%20For%20ISRO%20Is%20Off%20The%20Charts%20After%20Chandrayaan-3'%3A%20NASA%20Official%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20India-US%20joint%20mission%20to%20study%20climate%20change%20with%20the%20world's%20most%20expensive%20Earth%20imaging%20satellite%20is%20in%20its%20final%20stages%20and%20the%20launch%20is%20expected%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202024%2C%20a%20senior%20NASA%20official%20has%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20exclusively%20to%20NDTV%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Laurie%20Leshin%2C%20the%20Director%20of%20NASA's%20Jet%20Propulsion%20Laboratory%2C%20said%20the%20NASA-ISRO%20Synthetic%20Aperture%20Radar%20(NISAR)%20will%20also%20help%20in%20predicting%20hazards%20like%20earthquakes%20and%20tsunamis%2C%20and%20that%20respect%20for%20India's%20space%20programme%20is%20%26quot%3Boff%20the%20charts%26quot%3B%20after%20Chandrayaan-3.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPurpose%2C%20Impact%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENISAR%20is%20a%20low%20earth%20orbit%20observatory%20being%20developed%20by%20ISRO%20and%20NASA%2C%20which%20will%20map%20the%20entire%20Earth%20in%2012%20days%20and%20provide%20consistent%20data%20for%20understanding%20changes%20in%20the%20planet's%20ecosystems%2C%20ice%20mass%2C%20vegetation%2C%20sea%20level%20rise%2C%20groundwater%20levels%20and%20natural%20hazards%2C%20including%20earthquakes%2C%20tsunamis%2C%20volcanic%20eruptions%20and%20landslides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20how%20the%20satellite%20will%20make%20a%20difference%20in%20the%20life%20of%20the%20common%20man%2C%20Ms%20Leshin%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BUnderstanding%20how%20the%20Earth's%20surface%20is%20changing%20is%20really%20important%20for%20understanding%20the%20impacts%20of%20climate%20change...%20NISAR%20will%20allow%20us%20to%20observe%20with%20precision%20small%20changes%20in%20that%20surface.%20Everyone%20should%20care%20about%20melting%20ice%20sheets%20and%20changing%20forests%2C%20and%20earthquakes%20and%20volcanoes%2C%20so%20it%20really%20will%20impact%20people's%20lives%20everywhere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NASA%20official%20said%20watching%20things%20changing%20on%20the%20Earth's%20surface%20will%20help%20scientists%20understand%20the%20physics%20behind%20the%20change%20and%20better%20predict%20what%20is%20coming%20in%20the%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECollaboration%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20so%20thrilled%20with%20the%20collaboration%20between%20NASA%20and%20ISRO%20on%20NISAR.%20This%20is%20the%20biggest%20collaboration%20on%20something%20technological%20between%20our%20two%20nations%20and%20certainly%20the%20biggest%20collaboration%20in%20the%20history%20of%20space%20exploration%20between%20the%20US%20and%20India.%20I%20am%20sure%20this%20is%20the%20beginning%20of%20many%20more%20things%20to%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Leshin%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20one%20thing%20to%20talk%20about%20it%20at%20a%20very%20high%20level%20and%20leadership%20talking%20about%20collaboration%2C%20but%20we%20have%20had%2030%20or%2040%20engineers%20at%20a%20time%20here%20in%20Bengaluru%20working%20shoulder-to-shoulder%20with%20their%20ISRO%20colleagues%20for%20over%20nine%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScientists%20from%20ISRO%20also%20spent%20time%20working%20on%20the%20radar%20at%20the%20Jet%20Propulsion%20Laboratory%20in%20California%20and%20it%20%C2%A0was%20then%20brought%20to%20Bengaluru%20to%20be%20mated%20with%20the%20spacecraft.%20%26quot%3BOverall%2C%20the%20teams%20have%20worked%20together%20spectacularly%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Leshin%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BMany%20Ways%20To%20Success%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20NASA's%20key%20learnings%20from%20the%20collaboration%2C%20Ms%20Leshin%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20learning%20that%20there%20are%20many%20ways%20to%20be%20successful%20in%20space.%20We%20are%20learning%20from%20each%20other.%20If%20you%20talk%20to%20our%20colleagues%20at%20ISRO%2C%20they%20would%20say%20they%20have%20learnt%20from%20us%20and%20my%20colleagues%20say%20we%20have%20absolutely%20learnt%20from%20India%20in%20how%20they%20do%20their%20work.%20And%20that%20is%20good%20for%20everyone.%20Innovation%20loves%20new%20ideas%20coming%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jet%20Propulsion%20Laboratory's%20director%20said%20that%20respect%20for%20India's%20space%20programme%2C%20which%20was%20already%20high%2C%20has%20gone%20up%20after%20the%20historic%20success%20of%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20so%20impressed%20with%20Chandrayaan-3%20and%20the%20future%20plans%20for%20Indian%20space%20exploration%2C%20and%20we%20look%20forward%20to%20having%20many%20more%20partnerships%20between%20NASA%20and%20ISRO.%20The%20respect%20for%20India's%20space%20programme%20-%20it%20was%20already%20very%20high%20because%20India%20has%20accomplished%20so%20much%20in%20space%20-%20but%20now%20it's%20off%20the%20charts.%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELaunch%20Next%20Year%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20director%20said%20the%20launch%20of%20NISAR%20is%20expected%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202024%20and%20both%20space%20agencies%20have%20decided%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20it%20only%20when%20they%20are%20ready.%20The%20spacecraft%20will%20undergo%20a%20series%20o