0the%20highest%20motorable%20road%20in%20the%20world%2C%20in%20the%20film%20%3Cem%3EDhak%20Dhak%3C%2Fem%3E.%20With%20her%20on%20this%20ride%20were%20fellow%20actors%20Dia%20Mirza%2C%20Fatima%20Sana%20Sheikh%2C%20and%20Sanjana%20Sanghi.%20Earlier%20in%20September%2C%20she%20played%20an%20equally%20fascinating%20part%20in%20Vishal%20Bhardwaj%E2%80%99s%20series%20%3Cem%3ECharlie%20Chopra%20and%20The%20Mystery%20of%20Solang%20Valley%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2066%2C%20Ratna%20Pathak%20Shah%20is%20living%20her%20best%2C%20with%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20roles%20that%20tap%20into%20her%20talent.%20She%20is%20not%20the%20one-dimensional%20mother%20of%20the%20yesteryears%2C%20and%20is%20raring%20to%20go%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20in%20film%2C%20in%20an%20OTT%20show%20or%20the%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20she%20is%20back%20with%20an%20adaptation%20of%20Aleksei%20Arbuzov%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EOld%20World%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20on%20stage%20with%20Naseeruddin%20Shah.%20The%20last%20time%20the%20couple%20was%20seen%20together%20on%20stage%2C%20with%20just%20each%20other%2C%20was%20in%20%3Cem%3EDear%20Liar%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Enearly%20two%20decades%20ago.%20Directed%20by%20Arghya%20Lahiri%2C%20the%20play%20is%20set%20in%20a%20medical%20sanitorium%20and%20is%20a%20rumination%20on%20old%20age%20and%20all%20that%20it%20brings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20a%20doctor%20from%20Lucknow%2C%20she%20is%20a%20Parsi%20patient%20from%20Mumbai.%20Pathak%20Shah%20leans%20heavily%20on%20her%20Dadar%20Parsi%20Colony%20upbringing%2C%20where%20she%20was%20surrounded%20by%20Parsis%2C%20and%20the%20result%20is%20a%20quirky%20and%20endearing%20character.%20%3Cem%3EOld%20World%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20gentle%20and%20emotional.%20The%20characters%20bloom%2C%20and%20the%20Shahs%20shine%20once%20again.%20They%20reminisce%2C%20dance%2C%20sing%2C%20and%20speak%20of%20aging%20and%20love%20with%20rare%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20her%20cinematic%20pursuits%2C%20Pathak%20Shah%20never%20left%20the%20stage%2C%20returning%20at%20every%20chance%20she%20got%20to%20their%20company%20Motley%20Theatre.%20In%20an%20interview%2C%20she%20talks%20about%20%3Cem%3EDhak%20Dhak%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20working%20with%20Naseeruddin%20Shah%20over%20the%20years%2C%20the%20hope%20she%20places%20on%20OTT%20content%2C%20and%20her%20undying%20love%20for%20live%20performance.%20Below%20are%20the%20edited%20excerpts%20of%20the%20interview%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3Eve%20just%20had%20a%20big%20film%20release%20with%20%3Cem%3EDhak%20Dhak%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20what%20was%20that%20like%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOh%20yes%2C%20%3Cem%3EDhak%20Dhak%3C%2Fem%3E%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20good%20film.%20I%20enjoyed%20the%20experience%20of%20the%20making%20%5Bof%20the%20film%5D.%20I%20was%20concerned%20about%20how%20the%20final%20product%20would%20be%2C%20but%20I%20was%20very%20pleased%20with%20the%20result.%20It%20is%20a%20moving%20and%20effective%20film%2C%20so%20I%20am%20happy%20to%20have%20been%20a%20part%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3Eve%20been%20quite%20vocal%20about%20older%20actresses%20not%20getting%20the%20roles%20they%20deserve%20in%20films.%20Do%20you%20think%20that%20is%20changing%3F%20Does%20this%20hold%20in%20theatre%2C%20too%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20do%20think%20there%20have%20been%20changes.%20Many%20more%20interesting%20parts%20are%20being%20written%20for%20actors%20of%20all%20ages.%20I%20think%20we%20are%20seeing%20quite%20a%20special%20moment%20in%20our%20journey%20of%20film%2C%20television%2C%20and%20OTT.%20Television%20has%20lagged%20but%20OTT%20has%20made%20a%20huge%20impact%20with%20different%20kinds%20of%20stories%20being%20told%2C%20different%20kinds%20of%20actors%20being%20cast%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20new%20kinds%20of%20writing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20very%20hopeful.%20I%20am%20getting%20more%20interesting%20parts%20than%20my%20mother%20did%20at%20this%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20stage%20too%2C%20women%20of%20all%20ages%20have%20been%20writing%20material%20for%20themselves.%20We%20are%20not%20sitting%20down%20and%20waiting%20for%20others%20to%20write%20for%20us.%20Take%20Jyoti%20Dogra%20for%20example%2C%20or%20Divya%20Jagdale.%20They%20have%20been%20writing%20stories%20that%20mean%20things%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20theatre%20is%20becoming%20a%20much%20more%20democratic%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHaving%20worked%20with%20Naseeruddin%20Shah%20in%20both%20film%20and%20theatre%2C%20what%20do%20you%20enjoy%20most%20about%20working%20together%3F%20What%20have%20you%20learned%20from%20him%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20been%20working%20with%20Naseer%20since%201975%2C%20and%20in%20quite%20a%20few%20productions%20he%20has%20directed.%20I%20can%20say%20honestly%20that%20I%20have%20learned%20most%20of%20what%20I%20know%20about%20acting%20from%20working%20with%20him%2C%20watching%20him%20work%2C%20and%20doing%20the%20workshops%20that%20he%20conducts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20collaboration%20between%20us%20has%20been%20hugely%20beneficial%20for%20me.%20Naseer%20as%20a%20director%2C%20has%20been%20particularly%20wonderful%20for%20a%20play%20like%20%3Cem%3EIsmat%20Aapa%20Ke%20Naam%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20idea%20was%20his.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20believe%20we%20could%20pull%20it%20off%20beyond%20a%20few%20shows.%20After%20all%2C%20who%20would%20understand%20Urdu%20here%20in%20Mumbai%3F%20And%2022%20years%20later%2C%20we%20are%20still%20performing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20learned%20a%20lot%20during%20it.%20It%20clarified%20my%20ideas%20about%20acting%20and%20the%20craft%20%E2%80%93%20also%2C%20the%20purpose%20of%20it.%20For%20me%2C%20%3Cem%3EIsmat%20Aapa%20Ke%20Naam%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3EDear%20Liar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20have%20both%20been%20colleges%20of%20acting.%20They%20helped%20me%20develop%20as%20a%20person%20and%20as%20an%20actor.%20And%20Naseer%E2%80%99s%20part%20in%20both%20of%20them%20has%20been%20extraordinary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20he%20did%20not%20direct%20%3Cem%3EDear%20Liar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20we%20have%20spent%20a%20long%20time%20with%20it.%20Now%2C%20what%20we%20are%20both%20doing%20is%20significantly%20more%20mature%2C%20more%20watchable%2C%20and%20more%20meaningful%20to%20us%20than%20when%20we%20first%20started%20doing%20the%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20been%20an%20incredible%20journey%20and%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20Naseer%20has%20been%20a%20part%20of%20it%2C%20every%20step%20of%20the%20way.%20Sometimes%20showing%20the%20way%2C%20sometimes%20pulling%20me%20along%2C%20but%20always%20by%20my%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14115502%2FOld-World-7.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14115502%2FOld-World-7.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14115502%2FOld-World-7-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14115502%2FOld-World-7-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684639%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERatna%20Pathak%20Shah%2C%20on%20stage%20with%20Naseeruddin%20Shah%2C%20in%20an%20adaptation%20of%20Aleksei%20Arbuzov%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3Cem%3EOld%20World%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Photo%20provided%20by%20author.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20working%20together%2C%20do%20the%20lines%20between%20rehearsals%20and%20home%20blur%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20preparation%20continues%20after%20rehearsal%20time%2