he%202017%20IIM%20Act%20%E2%80%93%20was%20cleared%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20August%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20newly%20notified%20norms%2C%20the%20government%20has%20also%20changed%20the%20eligibility%20criteria%20for%20IIM%20directors%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Fnov%2F14%2Fcentre-takes-control-of-iims-president-to-pick-their-directors-2632661.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20new%20norms%20make%20a%20first%20class%20degree%20in%20in%20both%20Bachelor%E2%80%99s%20and%20Master%E2%80%99s%20mandatory%20along%20with%20a%20PhD%20or%20an%20equivalent%20qualification%20from%20a%20reputed%20institute%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20change%20has%20come%20in%20effect%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20controversy%20surrounding%20the%20reappointment%20of%20Dheeraj%20Sharma%20as%20IIM-Rohtak%E2%80%99s%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharma%20had%20misrepresented%20his%20academic%20credentials%20during%20his%20initial%20appointment%2C%20which%20occurred%20before%20the%20enactment%20of%20the%20IIM%20Act.%20He%20had%20a%20second%20class%20Bachelor%E2%80%99s%20degree%2C%20instead%20of%20a%20first%20class%2C%20which%20was%20a%20mandatory%20eligibility%20requirement%20for%20the%20job%20as%20per%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20advertisement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20education%20ministry%20found%20out%20about%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20deceptive%20actions%2C%20it%20was%20unable%20to%20prevent%20his%20re-appointment%20for%20a%20second%20term%20last%20year.%20This%20was%20because%2C%20at%20the%20time%20of%20his%20re-appointment%2C%20the%20IIM%20Rohtak%20Board%20had%20the%20absolute%20power%20under%20the%20IIM%20Act%20to%20choose%20the%20director%20and%20it%20had%20not%20stipulated%20a%20first-class%20Bachelor%E2%80%99s%20and%20Master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20as%20a%20mandatory%20criterion%2C%20an%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fpublic-interest-to-orders-ignored-govt-gets-power-to-dissolve-iim-boards-9022259%2F%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%20rules%2C%20the%20president%20will%20now%20have%20the%20powers%20to%20appoint%20and%20remove%20directors%20and%20dissolve%20the%20boards%2C%20if%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20revised%20process%2C%20the%20search%20and%20selection%20committee%20will%20submit%20a%20roster%20of%20three%20candidates%20under%20consideration%20for%20the%20directorial%20position%20to%20the%20Visitor.%20If%20the%20Visitor%20is%20not%20satisfied%20with%20the%20proposed%20names%2C%20they%20can%20seek%20fresh%20recommendations%20from%20the%20same%20committee%20or%20constitute%20a%20fresh%20search-cum-selection%20committee%20for%20the%20purpose%2C%20the%20notification%20issued%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIIM%E2%80%99s%20had%20resisted%20the%20provision%20of%20a%20Visitor%20in%202015%20when%20the%20draft%20of%20the%20IIM%20Act%20was%20released.%20They%20had%20maintained%20that%20the%20move%20would%20undermine%20their%20autonomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699941968000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14094307%2FIIMB_entrance.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Funion-govt-notifies-norms-giving-itself-absolute-control-on-iim-boards-appointment-of-directors%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20President%20of%20India%20will%20now%20be%20the%20Visitor%20of%20each%20IIM%2C%20through%20whom%20the%20government%20will%20have%20the%20final%20say%20in%20appointment%20of%20the%20boards'%20chairperson%20and%20director.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Funion-govt-notifies-norms-giving-itself-absolute-control-on-iim-boards-appointment-of-directors%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3