.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20Tanvi%20Srivastava.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699626225000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334021%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Inspired%20by%20Netaji%20Bose%2C%20Asha%20Sahay%20was%2017%20when%20she%20joined%20INA's%20Rani%20of%20Jhansi%20regiment%20and%20fought%20for%20Indian%20independence.%20Her%20great-granddaughter-in-law%2C%20Tanvi%20Srivastava%2C%20has%20documented%20her%20incredible%20story%20in%20the%20book%20'The%20War%20Diary%20of%20Asha-san'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IIT%20Madras%20NPTEL-GATE%20Portal%20Offers%20Free%20Resources%20to%20Prepare%20for%20the%20Exam%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(IIT)%20Madras%20is%20offering%20the%20NPTEL-GATE%20portal%20to%20students%20aspiring%20to%20ace%20the%20GATE%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Programme%20on%20Technology%20Enhanced%20Learning%20(NPTEL)%20%E2%80%94%20Graduate%20Aptitude%20Test%20in%20Engineering%20(GATE)%20portal%20provides%20access%20to%20previous%20years%E2%80%99%20questions%20from%202007%20to%202022%2C%20covering%20various%20exam%20topics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20institution%E2%80%99s%20press%20statement%20notes%20that%20every%20year%2C%20about%20seven%20to%2010%20lakh%20students%20in%20India%20take%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F217007%2Fgate-exam-topper-tips-akhand-swaroop-pandit-postgraduation-engineering-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGATE%20examination%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20in%202023%2C%20about%20seven%20lakh%20students%20registered%2C%20and%20about%20one%20lakh%20students%20successfully%20qualified.%20The%20