n%20what%20the%20authorities%20quoted%20(749)%2C%20informs%20Natasha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20this%20database%2C%20we%20could%20counter%20the%20claims%20of%20NHAI%20that%20these%20were%20very%20small%20and%20stunted%20trees%20and%20it%20would%20be%20no%20loss%20if%20they%20were%20axed.%20What%20we%20took%20to%20NGT%20was%20not%20just%20an%20emotional%20appeal%20but%20actually%20data%20backed%20with%20facts%20and%20figures.%20Also%2C%20anyone%20can%20replicate%20this%20method%20with%20little%20effort%20to%20geo-tag%20trees%20in%20their%20cities%20and%20hold%20authorities%20accountable%20when%20healthy%20trees%20are%20made%20to%20disappear%20overnight%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20citizens%E2%80%99%20group%20also%20sought%20help%20from%20several%20ministers%2C%20Members%20of%20Parliament%20(MPs)%2C%20and%20Members%20of%20the%20Legislative%20Assembly%20(MLAs)%2C%20Asiya%20says.%20But%20when%20no%20one%20in%20power%20listened%20to%20them%2C%20they%20approached%20the%20National%20Green%20Tribunal%20and%20filed%20a%20petition%20against%20the%20decision%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20three%20citizens%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Natasha%2C%20Pranay%20Juvvadi%2C%20and%20Tejah%20%E2%80%94%20became%20applicants%20in%20the%20case%2C%20the%20remaining%20citizens%20kept%20organising%20awareness%20campaigns%20across%20the%20city%20to%20make%20authorities%20understand%20why%20there%20was%20a%20need%20to%20save%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F138262%2Fpillalamarri-mahabubnagar-telengana-banyan-tree%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egiant%20trees%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-4-1-1699537213.jpg%5C%